NK131(do)003:1: // dris lan yang gsal sgron ma zhes btags pa gsang
NK131(do)003:2: sngags rnying mar log rtog spel ba gzhom byed rgyal
NK131(do)003:3: ba'i gsung bzhin legs par bshad pa lung gi rnga
NK131(do)003:4: chen zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK131(do)003:5: na mo gu ru b+h+yahbi dza yan+tu /
NK131(do)003:6: bden gsung tshad ma'i nyi ma rkang gnyis gtso //
NK131(do)003:7: bden pa'i mthar thug 'gog bden 'dus ma byas //
NK131(do)003:8: gang zhig bden pa mngon rtogs lam gyi chos //
NK131(do)003:9: de de'i mtshan nyid gang mnga' gtan gyi skyabs //
NK131(do)003:10: thugs rje'i bdag nyid rgyal bas gdul bya yi //
NK131(do)003:11: khams dbang bsam pa'i rjes mthun gsungs pa la //
NK131(do)003:12: phyogs lhung phrag dog gdon gyi kun dkris can //
NK131(do)003:13: snyigs dus bstan pa'i chu bur 'di gzhom bya //
NK131(do)003:14: mtha' bral mtha' la lhung ba'i rtog ge'i sprin //
NK131(do)003:15: chags sdang rlung gis sbar bas nges don gyi //
NK131(do)003:16: phrin las snang ba'i dkyil 'khor chud gsan par //
NK131(do)003:17: phyogs 'dir blo mchog byams 'jam dbyangs sogs /
NK131(do)003:19: de la re zhig ri bo dge ldan pa'i bstan
NK131(do)003:20: khrod du bzhugs pa'i brag dkar dge bshes bya ba
NK131(do)003:21: zhig gis nyams len gyi tshul la dris lan gyi
NK131(do)003:22: yi ge zhig mdzad pa mig lam du snang bar
NK131(do)003:23: gyur mod / blo dang ldan pa rnams dogs pa sel dgos pa mi 'dug kyang /
NK131(do)003:24: blo gros nyam chung ba rnams log par rtog pa'i
NK131(do)003:25: lam las bzlog pa'i phyir cung zad dpyad par bya'o
NK131(do)003:26: // de la khyed kyi yi ge der /
NK131(do)003:28: bla ma rin po che'i gzhi ni chos kyi blo mi skye /
NK131(do)003:29: chos byed 'dod cig byung ba'i tshe ro mtsho 'khor la brgyab pa lta bu'i mgo bo 'khor te /
NK131(do)003:31: bla ma rin po che'i gzhi ni chos kyi blo
NK131(do)003:32: mi skye zhes pa lta bu zhig las go rgyu
NK131(do)003:33: ma byung ba / rnam dbye sbyar ma shes pas 'brel med du gyur te /
NK131(do)003:35: gzhi nas zhes rnam dbye lnga pa sbyar na 'brel chags par 'gyur la /
NK131(do)003:37: mi 'dra ba la dpe ma grub //
NK131(do)003:38: 'dra ba de nyid dngos ma yin //
NK131(do)003:40: chos gang dang gang la dpe don mtshungs pa zhig
NK131(do)003:41: sbyar ba mkhas pa rnams la grags shing grub pas
NK131(do)003:42: ro la sems med pas mtsho la g.yeng bar mgo
NK131(do)003:43: 'khor ba'i 'du shes mi 'byung bas khyed la 'dri
NK131(do)003:44: ba po de 'du shes med pa zhig yin 'dra
NK131(do)003:45: bas bshad kyang go bar mi 'gyur la /
NK131(do)003:46: ro mtsho la bskyur ba'i mgo gcig pu 'khor ba ga la srid /
NK131(do)003:47: dpe don 'gal ba can spro ba'i rnam dpyod kyang khams che /
NK131(do)003:49: ji ltar byed mi shes par 'dug pa'i chos de /
NK131(do)003:51: chos zhig byed rgyu byung na bzang zhing ma byung
NK131(do)003:52: yang chog pa lta bu byed rkyen 'dug pa'i de
NK131(do)003:53: ltar yin nam / sogs 'brel med 'ga' zhig bris
NK131(do)003:54: 'dug pas mtshon yi ge 'di'i mgo mjug thams cad
NK131(do)003:56: rnam dbye sbyar tshul ma shes pa sdeb ma dag
NK131(do)003:57: pa sogs nor ba'i phung po smos kyis mi lang
NK131(do)003:58: bar spros 'dug pas dpyad par bya ba'i yul du
NK131(do)003:59: ma dmigs shing yig sde ba tsam yang mi mkhyen
NK131(do)003:60: bzhin du chos kyi tshul la dgag sgrub kyi thugs
NK131(do)003:61: khur de bzhag na legs par mngon no //
NK131(do)003:62: yang chos ni 'dzin pa la zer chos byed pa 'dzin pa'i thabs la 'bad pa yin /
NK131(do)003:63: zhes bris pa chos kyi sgra shes bya spyi la
NK131(do)003:64: 'jug pa khyod kyis lam dang myang 'das gcig pur
NK131(do)003:65: bsam nas smras pa'ang don ma rtogs te /
NK131(do)003:67: chos ni shes bya lam dang ni //
NK131(do)003:68: mya ngan 'das dang yid kyi yul //
NK131(do)003:69: bsod nams tshe dang gsung rab dang //
NK131(do)003:72: chos byed pa 'dzin pa'i thabs la 'bad par smra
NK131(do)003:73: ba'ang khyod rang gi go phyogs tsam ste mkhas pa
NK131(do)003:74: gzhan gyis bshad pa ma mthong ngo //
NK131(do)003:76: bde ba 'dod cing sdug bsngal chung ngu tsam yang
NK131(do)003:77: mi 'dod pa sha stag yin pa'i nges par chos
NK131(do)003:78: byed dgos / de las thabs gzhan med /
NK131(do)003:81: sdug bsngal chung ngu tsam yang mi 'dod pa sha stag yin pas /
NK131(do)003:82: bde ba'i thabs su nges par dam pa'i chos byed dgos /
NK131(do)003:83: de bas thabs gzhan gyis gtan gyi bde ba thob par mi nus /
NK131(do)003:84: zhes smras na go bde zhing 'dri ba po'i blo la nges par 'gyur gyi /
NK131(do)003:86: tshig kyang sde ba legs mi shes na //
NK131(do)003:87: don bzang smos kyang ci zhig dgos //
NK131(do)003:89: yang nor bsgoms na nong sangs rgyas /
NK131(do)003:90: nub bsgoms na nub sangs rgyas zer ba'i gdams ngag
NK131(do)003:91: zab mo yong gin 'dug pa de la yid brtan
NK131(do)003:92: rung ngam mi rung zhes khyed la dris 'dug pa
NK131(do)003:93: / khyed rang rnam pas bsgoms nas sangs rgyas mi thob par 'dod pa yin nam /
NK131(do)003:94: nged ni bsgoms na sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa yin te /
NK131(do)003:95: gsang sngags su ma zad mdo lam du'ang /
NK131(do)003:96: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal pas /
NK131(do)003:97: so skye drug khris bden pa mthong nas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob bo //
NK131(do)003:98: zhes zab mo'i chos thos pa'i mod la mthong lam rtogs par gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)003:99: byang chub sems dpa' de 'dod na zhag bdun gyis
NK131(do)003:100: bla na med pa'i rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par
NK131(do)003:101: byed do // zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)003:102: rdo rje 'chang gi lam ni myur zhing thabs la
NK131(do)003:103: ma rmongs pas mig 'phrul lta bus rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK131(do)003:104: rgyas kyi 'bras bu ster bar byed pa zhig ste
NK131(do)003:106: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod pa dang //
NK131(do)003:107: mtshams med lnga ni byed pa dang //
NK131(do)003:108: chom rkun las kyi longs spyod pa'ang //
NK131(do)003:110: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)003:111: zhes gsungs shing sngon du las ngan pa de dag
NK131(do)003:112: byed bzhin pa zhig yin yang sngags lam dang 'phrad
NK131(do)003:113: pa'i mod la sbyangs pa sngon du song ma song
NK131(do)003:114: ji ltar rung grol bar 'gyur ba myur lam 'di'i
NK131(do)003:115: khyad par gyi chos su grub pa las rnying ma
NK131(do)003:116: kho na'i khyad chos min pas thugs gu dog de
NK131(do)003:118: sngon gyi dus su b+ham ga la'i yul du rgyal
NK131(do)003:119: po ha ri tsan+d+ra 'khor stong phrag bcas rdo rje
NK131(do)003:121: o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti 'khor khri
NK131(do)003:122: phrag bcas rig 'dzin gyi sar gshegs pas o rgyan
NK131(do)003:123: gyi yul tsam stongs par grags pa dang /
NK131(do)003:124: sras pu tri gsum 'khor bdun brgya dang sras mo
NK131(do)003:125: go ma de ba'i 'khor brgya dang bcas pa rdo
NK131(do)003:126: rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i tshom bu tshogs
NK131(do)003:127: sgrub kyi rnal 'byor la brten nas rdo rje 'chang
NK131(do)003:128: gi sar gshegs pa'i tshul sher phyin tshul brgya lnga
NK131(do)003:129: bcu pa'i 'grel par gsungs shing slob dpon ye shes
NK131(do)003:130: bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i gzhung de nyid bstan 'gyur
NK131(do)003:131: gyi nang du bzhugs la rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu
NK131(do)003:132: 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni gsang sngags rnying ma'i tan+t+ra sde
NK131(do)003:133: bco brgyad kyi spyi rgyud dpal gsang ba snying po
NK131(do)003:134: yin te rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au ti dza'i khang thog
NK131(do)003:135: tu rgyud sde de rnams glegs bam gyi char babs
NK131(do)003:136: pa'i tshul der zhib mor yod pas ltos shig /
NK131(do)003:137: de bzhin du rgya bod kyi grub thob mchog rnams
NK131(do)003:138: nas tha na grub pa'i rtags mtshan phra mo tsam
NK131(do)003:139: zhig yan chad sngags lam la brten nas byung ba
NK131(do)003:140: kho na ste de thams cad bsgoms nas grol ba
NK131(do)003:142: de'ang bskyed rim gyi lam ji bzhin pa bsgoms pas
NK131(do)003:143: kyang rab zla ba gcig 'bring gsum tha mas drug
NK131(do)003:144: ji ltar yang spogs chog dang bcas pa'i zla ba
NK131(do)003:145: bcu gnyis nas dngos grub 'grub par rgyud sde rnams
NK131(do)003:146: nas mgrin gcig gis gsungs pa de nangs nub nam
NK131(do)003:147: bsgoms na sangs rgyas par gsungs pa ma yin nam
NK131(do)003:148: / gzhan yang dbang po rnon po kha cig bsgom
NK131(do)003:149: ma dgos par dbang dus kho nar grol ba in+d+ra
NK131(do)003:151: 'thag mkhan rnams kyi pha rgan rgas 'khog che bas
NK131(do)003:152: bu rnams ngo tsha nas mi mngon par sbas pa
NK131(do)003:153: zhig la grub thob dza lan+d+ha ri pas byin gyis
NK131(do)003:154: brlabs nas gdams ngag cung zad byin pa bsgoms pas
NK131(do)003:155: grol ba grub thob tan+ti par grags pa dang /
NK131(do)003:156: goo rak+sha ste ba lang rdzi bor grags pa dang /
NK131(do)003:157: zhing pa rtog rtse ba dang /
NK131(do)003:158: gdol pa'i bu ma tam gi dang /
NK131(do)003:159: dom+b+hi pa ste g.yung mo can dang /
NK131(do)003:160: bya li pa ste bya rngon pa sogs grub thob
NK131(do)003:161: ches che ba de thams cad kyis spyod pa tha
NK131(do)003:162: mal gyi tshul du gnas bzhin par bla ma'i man
NK131(do)003:163: ngag nangs bsgoms nangs rgyas nub bsgoms nub sangs rgyas
NK131(do)003:165: de bzhin du bod kyi ljongs su bstan pa snga
NK131(do)003:166: bar la slob dpon chen po'i thugs sras rje 'bangs
NK131(do)003:167: nyer lnga / mchims phu'i rtogs ldan brgyad cu /
NK131(do)003:168: yer ba'i grub thob brgya rtsa sogs dang /
NK131(do)003:169: bee ros khams su spang rgan po mi pham mgon
NK131(do)003:170: po dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa lnga lon pa zhig
NK131(do)003:171: byin gyis brlabs nas gdams ngag cung zad bstan pas
NK131(do)003:172: grol zhing dgung lo yang nyis brgya lhag bzhugs nas
NK131(do)003:173: mthar sku lus na bun ltar yal /
NK131(do)003:174: de'i slob ma ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan /
NK131(do)003:178: nyang shes rab 'byung gnas rnams gcig rting la gcig
NK131(do)003:179: wa seng ge brag sogs su sku na bun yal
NK131(do)003:180: ba ltar song / nyang ting 'dzin bzang po dang /
NK131(do)003:181: de'i slob ma sba ston blo gros dbang phyug /'brom rin chen 'bar /
NK131(do)003:182: ldang ma lhun grub rgyal mtshan /
NK131(do)003:183: lce btsun seng ge dbang phyug /
NK131(do)003:184: grub thob me long rdo rje sogs mang rab cig
NK131(do)003:185: gzugs sku zag med 'ja' lus su song ba grub
NK131(do)003:186: thob rnams kyi rnam thar tsam spyan 'og tu ma
NK131(do)003:187: chud pas chos skad 'di rnying ma kho na'i yin
NK131(do)003:188: par bsams nas chos dang gang zag thams cad la
NK131(do)003:189: skur pa tshan po che btab bo //
NK131(do)003:190: 'o na da lta grol bar mi nus pa ci yin snyam na /
NK131(do)003:191: deng sang ni dus snyigs ma'i mthar lhung /
NK131(do)003:192: gang zag gi blo stobs dang shes brtson 'grib /
NK131(do)003:193: gsang sngags zab mo'i chos dang lta spyod snod med la khrom bsgrags su byed /
NK131(do)003:194: gsang ba 'chal bas gang zag gi snod kyi skyon
NK131(do)003:195: la ltos nas chos kyi byin rlabs yal ba ltar
NK131(do)003:196: snang ba gsar rnying gnyis ka'i gang zag gi skyon
NK131(do)003:197: yin la chos kyi skyon ma yin te da lta'i
NK131(do)003:198: dus kyang ji bzhin sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK131(do)003:199: tshe 'adi'am bar dor grol bar bslu ba med de
NK131(do)003:200: / chos nyid kyi bden pa ni bri gang dang
NK131(do)003:201: bral bas 'dus byas kyi khams su nyams pa med
NK131(do)003:202: pas zab mo'i gnas la the tshom mi 'tshal lo
NK131(do)003:203: / // bsgoms na'ang sangs rgyas thob mi yong bsam
NK131(do)003:204: pa'i the tshom nyid dngos grub kyi gegs su che
NK131(do)003:205: / // bar gsungs te / bde ba can du
NK131(do)003:206: skye ba'i rgyu tshogs gzhan tshang yang the tshom gyi
NK131(do)003:207: blo skyes pas pad+ma'i kha mi bye bar lo grangs
NK131(do)003:208: du mar gnas par mdo las gsungs shing /
NK131(do)003:209: gsang sngags ni dad pa brtan na dbang po rno rtul gang gis kyang 'grub par bshad de /
NK131(do)003:211: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK131(do)003:212: don la the tshom med pa yi //
NK131(do)003:213: mkhas pa la ni dngos grub nye //
NK131(do)003:214: yang na blun po dad pa brtan //
NK131(do)003:215: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub nye //
NK131(do)003:216: rtog cing dpyod pa'i rtog ge pa //
NK131(do)003:217: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub med //
NK131(do)003:218: ces gsungs pa'i phyir gsang sngags ni rtog ge'i spyod
NK131(do)003:219: yul ma yin par rgyud sde thams cad nas gsungs
NK131(do)003:220: so // de ltar na dri ba po'i lan kho
NK131(do)003:221: bo cag gis chos dang mthun par btab zin pas
NK131(do)003:223: yang khyed kyis rnying ma'i bla ma yod bsdu med
NK131(do)003:224: bsdu g.yung ston khro rgyal dang rong pa lha dga'
NK131(do)003:225: bcas kyi / dbang po shin tu rno zhing bsod
NK131(do)003:226: nams rlabs chen dang ldan pa'i rje btsun mi la
NK131(do)003:227: bcas kyi / la / nong bsgoms na nong sangs rgyas /
NK131(do)003:228: nub bsgoms na nub sangs rgyas pa'i gdams ngag zab
NK131(do)003:229: shos de bstan 'dug kyang phan ma thub par gzhan
NK131(do)003:230: yang sangs rgyas thabs kyi gdams ngag gang yang bstan
NK131(do)003:231: rgyu ma byung bar gsar ma'i grub thob lho brag
NK131(do)003:232: mar pa'i mdun du gtong dgos byung 'dug pa'i /
NK131(do)003:234: bla ma dag gi rje btsun mi la la gdams
NK131(do)003:235: ngag bstan rgyu med nas lho brag mar pa'i mdun
NK131(do)003:236: du btang dgos byung ba yin min kha tshon chod
NK131(do)003:237: dka' ste / spyir gang zag gi rgyud tshod rdzogs
NK131(do)003:238: pa'i sangs rgyas ma gtogs gzhan gyis mi shes par
NK131(do)003:239: gsungs te gzhan sems mkhyen pa 'phags rgyud kyi mngon
NK131(do)003:242: 'od srungs nga dang 'dra ba ma gtogs gang zag gi tshod shes pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)003:243: zhes bka' stsal pa la dran pa mngon du gzhag dgos /
NK131(do)003:244: ye shes can rnams kyis gang zag so so'i tshe
NK131(do)003:245: rabs kyi 'brel pa yod pa'i lha dang bla ma
NK131(do)003:246: lung ston pa rgya bod kyi kun tu tshad mas
NK131(do)003:247: grub pa yin te 'phags yul du nag po bi
NK131(do)003:248: r+au pa la rdo rje phag mo mi mo'i rnam
NK131(do)003:249: par byon nas khyod kyi skye ba mang por las
NK131(do)003:250: 'brel yod pa bi r+au pa yin pas de ma
NK131(do)003:251: h+aa ra ta ra yod kyi der song gsungs pa'ang
NK131(do)003:252: gdams ngag med nas der btang ba yin nam /
NK131(do)003:253: slob dpon mtsho skyes la rdo rje phag mo rgan
NK131(do)003:254: mo'i tshul bzung nas khyed kyi tshe rabs kyi bla
NK131(do)003:255: ma grub thob phag tshang pa yin pas de'i gan
NK131(do)003:256: du song zhig ces gsungs pa'ang rdo rje phag mo
NK131(do)003:257: la gdams ngag bstan rgyu med pas yin nam /
NK131(do)003:258: grub chen l+au yi pas o di bi sha'i rgyal
NK131(do)003:259: po dang blon po gnyis la rgyal po khyod lho
NK131(do)003:260: phyogs ku ma ra k+she tra na smad 'tshong ma
NK131(do)003:261: 'di dang 'di lta bu yod kyi de'i g.yog gyis
NK131(do)003:262: gsungs shing / blon po la bram ze khyod sa
NK131(do)003:263: kwa na na ga ra na chang 'tshong ma 'di
NK131(do)003:264: lta bu zhig yod pas de'i g.yog gyis zhes gsungs
NK131(do)003:265: nas btang ba'ang gdams ngag bstan rgyu med pa dang
NK131(do)003:266: ma grol ba ga la yin /
NK131(do)003:267: slob dpon b+aa li ta p+aa des sangs rgyas ye
NK131(do)003:268: shes la bdag gis ni de kho na nyid ma
NK131(do)003:269: rtogs pas khyod ri bo rtse lngar song gsungs nas
NK131(do)003:270: phyin pa 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang 'phrad nas dngos
NK131(do)003:271: grub thob par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)003:272: rje phag mo grub pas thog mar sa chen gyi
NK131(do)003:273: drung du lam 'bras zhus shing bsgoms pas rje zhig
NK131(do)003:274: na bla ma zhang gis lung bstan pa ltar dwags
NK131(do)003:275: po snyi sgom gyi snyan pas thugs phrogs te dwags
NK131(do)003:276: lha sgam por byon nas rje de nyid kyi thugs
NK131(do)003:277: sras su gyur pa'ang sngon gyi las 'brel dang thugs
NK131(do)003:278: bskyed kyi khyad par las chos sgo de la brten
NK131(do)003:279: nas bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rlabs
NK131(do)003:280: po che 'byung bar gzigs pa las /
NK131(do)003:281: rje sa chen la gdams ngag med pa dang lam 'bras kyis nor ma nyan pa ga la yin /
NK131(do)003:282: rje btsun tsong kha pas bod kyi bshes gnyen thams
NK131(do)003:283: cad las gdams ngag yod dgu gsan kyang lho brag
NK131(do)003:284: grub chen las kyi rdo rje dang /
NK131(do)003:285: bla ma dbu ma pa la ma thug par yang
NK131(do)003:286: dag pa'i lta ba ji bzhin thugs rgyud la ma
NK131(do)003:287: 'khrungs par gsungs pa sngon du gang gsan pa'i chos
NK131(do)003:288: de rnams kyis ma grol ba ga la yin te
NK131(do)003:289: sngon gyi las 'brel zab pa'i bla ma de dag
NK131(do)003:290: dang 'phrad ma thag mngon par rtogs pa thams cad
NK131(do)003:291: sgo phye ba 'dra zhig sngon gyi mkhas grub thams
NK131(do)003:292: cad la byung bar gda' bas /
NK131(do)003:293: ye shes gzigs pa rnams kyi spyod yul dang /
NK131(do)003:294: rang re'i bem po'i rum gyi rnam shes kol le
NK131(do)003:295: ba'i 'char sgo gnyis bsgrig tu mi rung zhig 'grig
NK131(do)003:296: par yang dka' bas sems las chung ngur 'dug cig
NK131(do)003:298: lta ba rdzogs chen nyams bzhes kyi mthi ma yin te /
NK131(do)003:300: rdzogs pa chen pos mdun nas gzer //
NK131(do)003:301: phyag rgya chen pos rgyab nas gzer //
NK131(do)003:302: kha nas gdams ngag khrag tu skyugs //
NK131(do)003:304: sbyangs pa phyag chen la mdzad kyang nyams rtogs rdzogs
NK131(do)003:305: pa chen por 'khrungs pa nyid kyi rdo rje'i gsung
NK131(do)003:306: mgur thams cad du rdzogs chen gyi lta sgom spyod
NK131(do)003:307: 'bras kho na gsal hrig ger bzhugs pa mkhyen ldan
NK131(do)003:308: rnams kyis dpyod dang shes par yod pa de las
NK131(do)003:311: rnying rgyud sogs zhes dris pa dang /
NK131(do)003:312: khyod kyis lan du rnying rgyud deng sang bka' 'gyur
NK131(do)003:313: gyi par gral su 'khod pa rang rang gi 'dod
NK131(do)003:314: mos yin nam / sangs rgyas kyi bka' 'gyur gyi
NK131(do)003:315: gral min pa bu ston rin po che'i chos 'byung
NK131(do)003:316: du gsung yod pa'i der gzigs shig /
NK131(do)003:317: bka' 'gyur phyogs gcig tu bsgril nas zhu dag mdzad
NK131(do)003:318: pa po ni bu ston thams cad mkhyen pa yin
NK131(do)003:319: pa'i de las tshad 'dzugs pa gzhan su yang med
NK131(do)003:321: 'phags pa'i yul dang bod du bstan pa snga dar
NK131(do)003:322: gyi dus su gang zag rnams gsang ba srung ba
NK131(do)003:323: la blo brtan pas gsang sngags lkog tu nyams su
NK131(do)003:324: len pa las 'dod rgyal du spyod pa'i srol med
NK131(do)003:325: / khyad par bla med kyi rgyud rnams mngon mtshan
NK131(do)003:326: du bsgyur bar rgyal blon gyi bkas ma gnang bas
NK131(do)003:327: gsung rab dkar chag tu 'debs snga ba 'phang thang
NK131(do)003:328: ma dang ldan dkar ma dag tu gsang sngags kyi
NK131(do)003:329: rgyud rnams bka' gnyan pas ma bkod ces bshad /
NK131(do)003:330: rgyud sde bzhi dang khyad par gsang sngags rgyud sde gsum ni slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK131(do)003:331: bi ma la sogs kyis slob dpon bee ro tsa
NK131(do)003:332: na sogs sprul pa'i rje 'bangs snod ldan nyung shas
NK131(do)003:333: tsam la lkog chos su gnang nas bsgyur bshad mdzad
NK131(do)003:334: cing nyams su blangs pa las gzhan gyis mi shes
NK131(do)003:335: / so sos nyams su blangs nas grub pa thob
NK131(do)003:336: pa las dus gcig tu gang zag gnyis la ma
NK131(do)003:337: / spel / glegs bam rnams kyang so so'i sgrub
NK131(do)003:338: gnas dang bas matha'i dben gnas rnams su bzhugs pa
NK131(do)003:339: las thun mong du zur tsam yang ma grags so
NK131(do)003:340: / spel / // gzhan pa'i sde snod gsum gyi gsung rab phal mo che dang /
NK131(do)003:342: byams chos dang thogs med klu sgrub sogs kyi gzhung
NK131(do)003:343: chen po phal che ba rnying ma'i dus bsgyur ba
NK131(do)003:344: ma gtogs pa'i bka' dang bstan bcos cher mi bzhugs
NK131(do)003:345: pa de dag gi 'gyur byang tsam la gzigs dang
NK131(do)003:346: shes so // bu ston rin po che'i bka' 'gyur
NK131(do)003:347: dkar chag tu med pa tsam gyis chos ma yin
NK131(do)003:349: rgyu mtshan gang gi phyir na spyir theg pa chen
NK131(do)003:350: po dang khyad par gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde ni
NK131(do)003:351: sangs rgyas nyid kyi spyod yul las sa bcu'i dbang
NK131(do)003:352: phyug chen po rnams kyis kyang tshad gzung bar mi
NK131(do)003:355: rnal 'byor rgyud rnams kyi ni tshad //
NK131(do)003:356: bye ba phrag ni drug nges te //
NK131(do)003:357: de bzhin rnal 'byor ma rgyud grangs //
NK131(do)003:358: bye ba phrag ni bcu drug grags //
NK131(do)003:359: theg chen las gzhan mdo sde rnams //
NK131(do)003:360: dung phyur phrag brgyad gsungs pa yin //
NK131(do)003:361: de bzhin pha rol phyin pa'i tshul //
NK131(do)003:362: sa ya dang ni dung phyur lnga //
NK131(do)003:364: gsang sngags phyi pa la yang /
NK131(do)003:365: lha dang lha min rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK131(do)003:366: gsang sngags rig sngags rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK131(do)003:367: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK131(do)003:368: rig 'dzin sde snod du ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK131(do)003:370: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa las /
NK131(do)003:371: bya ba'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi /
NK131(do)003:372: spyod pa'i rgyud stong phrag brgyad /
NK131(do)003:373: rtog pa'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi /
NK131(do)003:374: gnyis ka'i rgyud stong phrag drug /
NK131(do)003:375: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud stong phrag bcu gnyis te /
NK131(do)003:376: rgyas par phye na grangs med do //
NK131(do)003:377: zhes 'byung ba'i phyir rgyud sde de rnams kyi nang
NK131(do)003:378: nas nyung shas tsam zhig rgya gar sogs yul dang
NK131(do)003:379: yul phran rnams su babs pa de las cung zad
NK131(do)003:380: tsam zhig bod kyi ljongs 'dir byung ba yin mchi
NK131(do)003:381: / de las kyang yul gyi dbus lag mthil tsam
NK131(do)003:382: du ma grags shing ma mthong ba tsam la blo
NK131(do)003:383: gtad nas bdag nyid kyi spyod yul du gyur pa
NK131(do)003:384: 'di kho na bden gyi gzhan ni mi bden zhes
NK131(do)003:385: dam bca' ba ni mtha' gcig tu zhen pa'i blo
NK131(do)003:386: rgya chung ba'i gtam shor ba mtshang che ste /
NK131(do)003:387: rgya gar du ma grags pa'i rgyud sde rnams /
NK131(do)003:390: d+ha nya ka da ka'i gling dang /
NK131(do)003:393: sa ra ha sogs grub thob rnams kyis blangs te
NK131(do)003:394: rang dang skal ba ldan pa re gnyis la bstan
NK131(do)003:395: nas bsgoms pas grub pa thob /
NK131(do)003:396: da lta bod bzhin khrom bsgrags su byed pa med
NK131(do)003:397: pas dngos grub myur du thob pa'i rgyu yang de
NK131(do)003:398: nyid yin la / rgya gar pa la yang rgyus
NK131(do)003:399: med na bod kyi lo ts+aa ba res rgya gar
NK131(do)003:400: gyi yul chen yul phran rnams su ci 'dra yod
NK131(do)003:402: jo bo rje a ti shas bsam yas kyi rgya
NK131(do)003:403: dpe rnams gzigs nas pha la pha la theg pa
NK131(do)003:404: chen po 'di la mtha' yod yod mi 'dra de
NK131(do)003:405: dus bod du bstan pa dar ba tsam rgya gar
NK131(do)003:407: slob dpon pad+mas sh+r+ai na len+d+ra dang mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod dang /
NK131(do)003:408: sde brgyad kyi gnas sogs nas rdzu 'phrul gyis blangs
NK131(do)003:409: pa'i rgyud sde mang po 'dug pas rgya gar las
NK131(do)003:410: bod na mang ba yin gsungs nas dpe 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)003:411: zhal bshus nas rgya gar du bskur bar mdzad pa
NK131(do)003:412: jo bo'i lam yin chen mor ltos dang gsal lo
NK131(do)003:413: // khyad par rdzogs chen rgya gar du ma grags par smras pa'ang /
NK131(do)003:414: dpal rdo rje sems dpas sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje la byin gyis brlabs /
NK131(do)003:415: des 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi sprul pa slob dpon 'jam
NK131(do)003:416: dpal bshes gnyen la brda yi sgo nas bstan cing
NK131(do)003:417: 'das rjes zhal chems kyi tshul du babs /
NK131(do)003:418: de la slob dpon sh+r+ai ri sing ha dang rim par /
NK131(do)003:419: dz+ny+aa na su tra bi ma la mi tra'i bar
NK131(do)003:420: chig brgyud du brda'i sgo nas bstan cing rig 'dzin
NK131(do)003:421: gong ma de dag gzugs sku mi snang ba'i tshe
NK131(do)003:422: / gdams ngag zhal chems 'das rjes kyi tshul du
NK131(do)003:423: babs pa rim bzhin dgongs pa dang snyan brgyud tsam
NK131(do)003:424: las tshigs dang yi ger ma bzhag pas rgya gar
NK131(do)003:425: pa rnams la yongs grags ci la yod /
NK131(do)003:426: bod kyi rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa'i thugs bskyed
NK131(do)003:427: dang gdul bya'i bsod nams kyis pan chen pad+ma sam
NK131(do)003:428: b+ha wa dang / mkhas pa bi ma la mi
NK131(do)003:429: tra spyan drangs pa'i thugs rje las slob dpon de
NK131(do)003:430: dag gi dngos slob skal ba mchog dang ldan pa
NK131(do)003:431: re gnyis la phyung ba mchog tu zab pa rdzogs
NK131(do)003:432: pa chen po'i skor rnams rang gis nyams su blangs
NK131(do)003:433: nas mchog gi dngos grub thob pa'i shul du gdams
NK131(do)003:434: ngag gi dpe tsam yang bzhag pa med par gter
NK131(do)003:435: du sbas pa slad kyi las can dag gis skal
NK131(do)003:436: ba dang smon lam gyi mthus rnyed de gang zag
NK131(do)003:437: re res gcig brgyud du nyams su blangs pa las
NK131(do)003:438: gzhan thun mong gi mkhas blun thams cad la da
NK131(do)003:439: lta'i dus bzhin ngo ma chos byed srol med cing
NK131(do)003:440: yongs su grags pa ma yin pas so //
NK131(do)003:441: de'i phyir bod kyi yul phran dang sgrub gnas rnams
NK131(do)003:442: su mi mngon par bzhugs pa'i rgyud sde 'ga' zhig
NK131(do)003:443: yul dbus kyi mkhas pa dag gi spyan lam du
NK131(do)003:444: ma chud pa'am / chud kyang thun mong gi spyod
NK131(do)003:445: yul dang mi 'tshams par dgongs te gud du bzhag
NK131(do)003:446: pa ji ltar rung phyi 'gyur gyi rgyud sde rtsod
NK131(do)003:447: med 'ga' zhig kyang da lta'i bka' 'gyur gyi khrod
NK131(do)003:448: du ma tshud de tsa mi dang sga los bsgyur
NK131(do)003:449: ba'i nag po chen po'i rgyud 'ga' zhig dpal ldan
NK131(do)003:450: 'brug pa bka' brgyud la grags pa dang /
NK131(do)003:451: gzhan yang grub thob khyung po rnal 'byor la bka'
NK131(do)003:452: babs pa'i ni gu'i chos skor rgya gzhung rtsod med
NK131(do)003:453: 'ga' dang / mkha' 'gro seng gdong dang phyag rdor
NK131(do)003:454: gyi rgyud dang sgrub sde sangs rgyas kyi bka' dngos
NK131(do)003:455: ma bod kyi bka' bstan 'gyur du med pa mang
NK131(do)003:456: po bzhugs shing de thams cad bka' ma yin par
NK131(do)003:458: pa'i chos tshul dang grub mtha' re bzhag nas gzhan
NK131(do)003:459: lugs dgag par mdzad pa ni bod kyi mkhas pa
NK131(do)003:461: de dag la dgos pa dang dgongs gzhi re yod pa gor ma chags shing /
NK131(do)003:462: rang re blo dman rnams kyi phyogs rgyug gis de
NK131(do)003:463: dag gi rjes su 'brangs nas dgag sgrub kyi lad
NK131(do)003:464: mo zlos pas chos spong gi g.yang sar nyams nyes
NK131(do)003:465: pang 'gyur ba stag mchongs sar was mchongs pas nyams
NK131(do)003:466: par gyur pa ltar la bag yod bya bar rigs
NK131(do)003:467: so // des na gsar ma rang gi chos kyi
NK131(do)003:468: drag shos thog mar mkhas mchog smri tis sgra rang
NK131(do)003:469: so // 'gyur mdzad / de nas lo ts+aa ba dge slong chos kyi blo gros kyis bsgyur cing /
NK131(do)003:470: phyis su sgra ba thugs rje seng ges nyang stod
NK131(do)003:471: rgyal mkhar rtser bsgyur ba'i rgya dpe dngos ma yod
NK131(do)003:472: bzhin pa'i gsang 'dus gnyis med rnam rgyal gyi rgyud
NK131(do)003:473: chen po dang / 'brog mi lo ts+aa bas 'gyur
NK131(do)003:474: yon la gser zho sum brgya phul nas pan chen
NK131(do)003:475: ga ya d+ha ras gnang ba dang /
NK131(do)003:476: phyis bod du byon tshe kha rag gnyos lo ts+aa
NK131(do)003:477: ba la gnang nas rgya dpe mang mkhar mu gu
NK131(do)003:478: lung du yod pa de mchog ra li so gnyis
NK131(do)003:479: dag kyang bu ston rin po che sogs rgyud yang
NK131(do)003:480: dag ma yin par gsungs pa dang de dag gi
NK131(do)003:481: lad mo dpal 'dzin gyis zlos nas /
NK131(do)003:482: gsang 'dus gnyis med rnam rgyal che //
NK131(do)003:483: rdo rje 'jigs byed sam lugs dang //
NK131(do)003:484: bde mchog ra li sum cu gnyis //
NK131(do)003:485: dus 'khor lce spyang glu gar dang //
NK131(do)003:486: kyee rdor sku gsung thugs gsang mdzod //
NK131(do)003:487: phyag na rdo rje mi g.yo ba //
NK131(do)003:488: rdo rje phag mo seng gdong ma //
NK131(do)003:489: phyag rgya chen po'i rgyud 'ga' dang //
NK131(do)003:490: mgon po dang ni lha mo'i rgyud //
NK131(do)003:491: brgya dang lnga bcu lhag la sogs //
NK131(do)003:492: rang bzos rdzun rgyud du ma snang //
NK131(do)003:493: rdo rje snying po'i smad 'grel dang //
NK131(do)003:494: lho pa thams cad mkhyen pa yis //
NK131(do)003:495: n+aa ro 'grel chen zhes pa'ang byas //
NK131(do)003:497: mkha' 'gro ma seng+ge'i gdong can bla ma pa ri
NK131(do)003:498: lo tsas rgya gar nas spyan drangs te dpal sa
NK131(do)003:499: skya pa la bka' babs pa'i rgya gzhung rtsod med
NK131(do)003:501: 'jigs byed sam lugs sogs rgyud sde phyed dang nyis brgya rdzun rgyud du bsgrags pa dang /
NK131(do)003:502: n+aa ro 'grel chen thog mar dpyal lo chos bzang
NK131(do)003:503: gis bsgyur nas stod smad kun tu nyi zla ltar
NK131(do)003:505: dus phyis pan+di ta nags kyi rin chen gyis yar
NK131(do)003:506: klung du bsgyur cing bshad pa'i rgya dpe deng sang
NK131(do)003:507: bzhugs par mkhas pa rnams gsungs shing /
NK131(do)003:508: de bzhin du 'gos khug pa lhas btsas kyis slob
NK131(do)003:509: dpon pad+ma'i thugs dam gshin rje pra khog snang gi
NK131(do)003:510: rgyud gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis byas /
NK131(do)003:511: zhes 'byams yig tu bris pa la /
NK131(do)003:512: rgyud de slob dpon sh+aan+ti pas spyod rgyud du bkral
NK131(do)003:513: cing grub thob dpal 'dzin gyis bya rgyud du bzhed
NK131(do)003:514: de rgya dpe'i dngos pos sngags log sun 'byin gyi
NK131(do)003:515: gsung thams cad ro la brgya shal gcig gis thong
NK131(do)003:516: mar btang ngo // 'bri gung dpal 'dzin gyis 'gos kyi 'byams yig gi rjes zlos bskyar nas /
NK131(do)003:517: rma ban rin chen mchog ces pas //
NK131(do)003:518: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud brtsams pas //
NK131(do)003:519: rgyal pos chad pa byung dogs nas //
NK131(do)003:520: lo grangs bcu gnyis gab ces grags //
NK131(do)003:521: zhes gsang ba snying po bod kyis brtsams par bsgrags /
NK131(do)003:522: rgyud de thog mar slob dpon pad+ma dang rmas bsgyur /
NK131(do)003:523: de nas bi ma la dang gnyags kyis bsgyur /
NK131(do)003:524: dus phyis bsam yas su slob dpon gyi phyag dpe
NK131(do)003:525: kha che pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai'i phyag tu byung ba
NK131(do)003:526: rta ston gzi brjid la babs /
NK131(do)003:527: de nas sha gad lo ts+aa ba la byung ba
NK131(do)003:528: bcom ldan ral gri la phul ba de'i yi ger
NK131(do)003:529: / rgyud kun snying po dpal ldan 'dus pa dang //
NK131(do)003:530: dbyer med rgyud chen 'di lta bu dang gzhan //
NK131(do)003:531: zab mo'i rgyud dang theg chen chos rnams dang //
NK131(do)003:532: 'jal nas tshul bzhin sgrub pa byed par shog /
NK131(do)003:534: mkhas mchog bcom ldan ral gris //
NK131(do)003:535: gnas gtsang steng gi 'og min nyams dga' bar //
NK131(do)003:536: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa'i bka' //
NK131(do)003:537: rgyud rgyal gsang snying rgya dpe ma rnyed pas //
NK131(do)003:538: bod kyis byas zhes gangs ri'i khrod 'dir grags //
NK131(do)003:539: bcom ldan ral gris rgya dpe legs btsal na //
NK131(do)003:540: gzhung 'di 'dzin pa'i sngags 'chang rnams la bstan //
NK131(do)003:541: pan chen bi shwa mi tra la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)003:542: gzhung gi sgrub byed gsang snying sgrub par ltos //
NK131(do)003:543: rgya bod gnyis su mkhas par legs sbyangs pas //
NK131(do)003:544: dpe 'di ma rnyed yid bzhin nor bu 'dra //
NK131(do)003:545: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi shwa mi tra yis //
NK131(do)003:546: gsang snying rgyud dang mthun pa'i 'grel pa mdzad //
NK131(do)003:547: 'di gnyis spangs nas rang gar 'chad pa rnams //
NK131(do)003:548: shes rab 'chal bas rang gzhan bslus pa yin //
NK131(do)003:550: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon bi shwa mi tras mdzad pa las /
NK131(do)003:551: ye shes sems dpa' gang reg pa /
NK131(do)003:554: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang mu med par gzhi
NK131(do)003:555: tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba
NK131(do)003:556: la / zhes pa sogs gsang snying ltar bkral ba dang /
NK131(do)003:557: slob dpon brgya byin sdong pos sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor
NK131(do)003:558: gyi 'grel chen du gsang snying gi lung drangs shing
NK131(do)003:560: rdo rje bzhad pa'i gsang 'dus kyi 'grel par yang /
NK131(do)003:561: rgyud 'di'i lung mang du drangs shing bstan bcos de
NK131(do)003:562: rnams ni bu ston thams cad mkhyen pa sogs kyis
NK131(do)003:563: tshad mar mdzad nas bstan 'gyur du bzhugs bzhin pa
NK131(do)003:564: dang / dus phyis bal po thang b+hi ha ra
NK131(do)003:565: nas glo bo lo ts+aa ba dpal ldan byang chub
NK131(do)003:566: kyis gsang snying gi rgya dpe rnyed pa las 'bri
NK131(do)003:567: gung lo ts+aa ba ma ni ka sh+r+ai dz+ny+aa nas
NK131(do)003:568: dang / bsgyur cing / kha cig rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis ma gsungs pa'i //
NK131(do)003:569: chos min rnams la chos su chags shing zhen //
NK131(do)003:570: kha cig rnam dag chos dang rgyud la yang //
NK131(do)003:571: yang dag min zhes the tshom som nyi za //
NK131(do)003:572: de 'dra'i log rtog sel bar bya ched dang //
NK131(do)003:573: rnam dag rgyud la bstod cing bkur ba'i phyir //
NK131(do)003:574: zhes ched du brjod pa dang /
NK131(do)003:575: bu ston rin po che'i bla ma thar pa lo
NK131(do)003:576: ts+aa nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyis gsang snying rgyud phyi
NK131(do)003:577: ma dang bcas pa la 'gyur mdzad nas dar rgyas
NK131(do)003:579: dpal 'dzin sogs kyis bod mar bsgrags pa'i rdzun phug
NK131(do)003:580: rgya dpe dang rgya gzhung rtsod med rnams kyis gtibs
NK131(do)003:581: pas bod rnams kha rog ste 'dug go //
NK131(do)003:582: bod kyis brtsams pa'i lung 'dren rgya gzhung rtsod med
NK131(do)003:583: rnams su yod don mchis sam gzu bor gnas pa'i
NK131(do)003:584: blo ldan rnams kyis bsam mno mdzad 'tshal /
NK131(do)003:585: des na sdang zhugs kho na'i dbang gis rnying ma
NK131(do)003:586: bkag par rlom pa'i snga phyi'i rtsod pa byung ba
NK131(do)003:587: thams cad 'di 'dra'i rigs can kho na ste 'tshang
NK131(do)003:588: brtol bar sla ba kho na'o //
NK131(do)003:589: 'on kyang sems can gyi las tshul ldog par dka'
NK131(do)003:590: bas sangs rgyas dngos bzhugs dus kyang kun tu rgyu
NK131(do)003:591: rnams kyis sangs rgyas la kha zer ba dang /
NK131(do)003:592: theg chen gyi sde snod rnams sangs rgyas kyi gsung ma yin par nyan thos rnams 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)003:593: klu sgrub la lung bstan ngan pa bcos te gsung rab kyi nang du bcug pa sogs /
NK131(do)003:594: slob dpon phyogs kyi glang pos /
NK131(do)003:595: phyin ci log la mtha' med phyir //
NK131(do)003:596: de dag 'dir ni spro bya min //
NK131(do)003:597: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtha' dag par brjod kyis mi lang zhing /
NK131(do)003:598: sems can gyi rnam par rtog pa la zad pa'i
NK131(do)003:599: mtha' mi dmigs pas skyon ltar snang ba'i sgro skur
NK131(do)003:600: gyi blo rtog kyang mi zad par shes par bya'o
NK131(do)003:601: // de bzhin du dpal dus kyi 'khor lor nyi zla shar du 'gro ba dang /
NK131(do)003:602: rgya nag bod kyi byang du yod par gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:603: la 'gos kyi bu chen rngog ston wa ba can
NK131(do)003:605: bcom ldan ral gris dus 'khor du 'jig rten gyi
NK131(do)003:606: bkod pa mngon pa dang mi mthun par gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:607: la phyi rol pa'i 'dod gzhung dang mthun zhes dgag
NK131(do)003:608: pa dang / red mda' pa gzhon nu blo gros
NK131(do)003:609: kyis bstan 'dzin rnams la 'phrin du gsol ba las
NK131(do)003:610: pa dang / / dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs sa bcu yis //
NK131(do)003:611: dbang phyug rnams kyis mdzad par grags na yang //
NK131(do)003:612: rigs dang mi rigs rnam dbye blo ldan gyis //
NK131(do)003:613: rnam par dpyad na 'thad pa'i tshul ma mthong //
NK131(do)003:614: rtsa ba'i rgyud la e wam gnyis yig med //
NK131(do)003:615: bsdus pa'i brgyud la 'gal ba du ma mthong //
NK131(do)003:616: gang nas blangs pa'i khungs kyang mi snang na //
NK131(do)003:617: 'phyon ma'i bu bzhin 'di la su yid rton //
NK131(do)003:619: de ltar nyes pa'i tshogs kun mthong gyur kyang //
NK131(do)003:620: da dung 'di la mngon zhen mi ldog na //
NK131(do)003:621: 'di yi sgrub byed don du mna' chu 'thung //
NK131(do)003:622: de las gzhan pa'i sgrub byed yod re kan //
NK131(do)003:623: zhes sogs dus kyi 'khor lo rgyal ba'i bka' ma
NK131(do)003:624: yin par dgag pa rgya cher 'bad pas byas pa
NK131(do)003:625: dang / ma mo rol pa'i rgyud dkrugs pas //
NK131(do)003:626: ga ya d+ha ra'i gser chos byung //
NK131(do)003:628: lam 'bras dang dgyes rdor la dgag pa byas shing /
NK131(do)003:629: pha dam pa'i zhi byed dang gcod yul rnams kyang yang dag ma yin par kha zer ba dang /
NK131(do)003:630: sa pan gyis phyag chen dang chos drug sogs dwags po bka' rgyud bkag pa dang /
NK131(do)003:631: ma cig lab sgron gyi gcod yul rnams la'ang ma
NK131(do)003:632: jo smyon pa'i rdol chos zhes kha cig gis bkag
NK131(do)003:633: pa dang / sa skya'i mkhas pa go sh+aaka stag
NK131(do)003:634: gsum gyis rje tsong kha pa'i lta ba dang grub
NK131(do)003:635: mtha' la 'gal khur bco brgyad sogs 'phangs shing dgag
NK131(do)003:636: pa tshan po che byas pa dang /
NK131(do)003:637: zhal gzigs kyi 'jam dbyangs kyang ji bzhin min par brjod pa dang /
NK131(do)003:638: mgon po phyag drug pa bon skyong du 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)003:639: bka' gdams gong ma rnams kyis sngags lam la 'jug pa nan gyis bkag pa dang /
NK131(do)003:640: bka' gdams pa 'ga' zhig gis grub chen nag po spyod pa la yang kha zer ba dang /
NK131(do)003:641: rgya gar du nyan thos sen+d+he pa rnams kyis theg
NK131(do)003:642: pa chen po'i srol 'byed dpal mgon klu sgrub la
NK131(do)003:643: skur pa mi bzad pa btab pa'i tshig gsung rab
NK131(do)003:645: sde snod gsum du ma bsdus dang //
NK131(do)003:646: lam gzhan nye bar ston phyir dang //
NK131(do)003:647: theg chen sangs rgyas gsung ma yin //
NK131(do)003:648: rig byed mtha' yi lta ba bzhin //
NK131(do)003:649: zhes pa ltar theg chen rgyal ba'i bka' ma yin
NK131(do)003:650: par nan gyis dgag pa'i rtsod pa'i yi ge mang
NK131(do)003:651: po byung ba 'phags mchog klus dpe thams cad bsdus
NK131(do)003:652: nas sa 'og tu sbas pa dang /
NK131(do)003:653: rgyal ba byams pas theg chen bkar sgrub mdzad pa
NK131(do)003:654: bzhin bod kyi mkhas rmongs thams cad kyis dgag pa
NK131(do)003:655: byas tshad chos min par 'gyur na yang dag pa'i
NK131(do)003:657: rang re lta bu'i blo dman rnams kyis de dag
NK131(do)003:658: gi rjes su 'brangs te dgag sgrub kyi lad mo
NK131(do)003:659: byed khul gyis chos spong gi sgrib pa'i g.yang sa
NK131(do)003:660: nyam nga bar tsham tshom med par ma mchongs shig
NK131(do)003:661: / gzhan yang rnying ma'i rgyud gzhan ma dag na /
NK131(do)003:662: yang phur gnyis sger du dag don med cing de
NK131(do)003:663: dag snga nas da lta'i bar dpal ldan sa skya
NK131(do)003:664: pa'i yab chos su song bas rnying ma 'gog rlom
NK131(do)003:665: rnams kyis ci yang ma smras pa chos bdag po'i
NK131(do)003:666: gzi byin gyis bsrungs pas kyang ltar snang gi rtsod
NK131(do)003:667: pa rnams 'jig par slab pa yin no //
NK131(do)003:669: deng sang gza' btsan gshin rje sogs sgrub mchod nyin
NK131(do)003:670: mtshan du byas te ngan sngags dang mthu gtad sogs
NK131(do)003:671: byed pa sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung ba i
NK131(do)003:672: yin / zhes dris pa'i lan du slob dpon pad+ma'i lung dang /
NK131(do)003:673: rje btsun mi la'i gsung drangs nas /
NK131(do)003:674: phra ba gshin rje gza' btsan sogs pho 'dre rnams dang /
NK131(do)003:675: phra men mo 'dre yin zer ba dang /
NK131(do)003:676: de dag la mchod bstod byed pa bsod nams dman pa yin gsungs /
NK131(do)003:678: gshin rje dang gza' btsan sogs mchod pa rnying ma
NK131(do)003:679: kho nar bsams nas smras pa'ang gzu bor mi gnas
NK131(do)003:681: gshin rje chos rgyal dang ya ma r+aa tsa bee
NK131(do)003:682: b+ha sa t+wa sogs ming gi rnam grangs yin pa
NK131(do)003:683: dang / gza' ni sa dge gnyis ka'i thun mong
NK131(do)003:684: min pa'i yi dam rta mgrin yang gsang khros pa
NK131(do)003:685: gter ston gsum gyi gter kha las byon pa'i bka'
NK131(do)003:686: srung ging lnga gza' gdong yin pa dang /
NK131(do)003:687: lo chen rin chen bzang po'i bka' srung pu tra ming sring /
NK131(do)003:688: ba ri lo ts+aa ba'i dbyu gu mched gsum /
NK131(do)003:689: dpang lo ts+aa ba'i chos bdag 'od 'bar /
NK131(do)003:690: rgyan gong gi rdo rje rab brtan ma /
NK131(do)003:692: rje btsun mi la'i tshe ring mched lnga /
NK131(do)003:694: 'brug pa'i rdo rje g.yu sgron ma /
NK131(do)003:695: gnod sbyin zangs kyi beg+tse can /
NK131(do)003:698: thang chen bshan pa lag dmar /
NK131(do)003:699: btsan rgod kha che dmar po /
NK131(do)003:701: dge lugs la grags pa'i tha 'og rgyal po /
NK131(do)003:702: 'bras spungs gnas chung rdo rje grags ldan /
NK131(do)003:703: se ra'i bya khrid mig gcig /
NK131(do)003:704: la mo'i tshangs pa dung thod can sogs gsar rnying
NK131(do)003:705: gi chos skyong de thams cad la la rgyal ba
NK131(do)003:708: o rgyan rin po che sogs kyis dkyil 'khor du bcug nas dbang bskur /
NK131(do)003:712: lag tu rdo rje byin nas bstan pa bsrung ba dang /
NK131(do)003:713: gang zag chos bzhin spyod pa rnams skyong bar gnyer gtad nas bstan pa'i srung mar bskos /
NK131(do)003:714: la la grub thob khyad par can rnams kyis dam la btags pa'i srung ma yin /
NK131(do)003:715: de thams cad kyang thog mar 'jig rten rang rgyud
NK131(do)003:716: pa la rgyal ba'i ye shes kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK131(do)003:718: dug la sngags kyis btab pa bzhin rgyud 'gyur bas
NK131(do)003:719: ngo bo ye shes yin kyang rnam pa dregs byed
NK131(do)003:720: lha srin sde brgyad kyi tshul du gnas pas sngon
NK131(do)003:721: gyi dam pa rnams kyis bstan cing mchod byar bzhag
NK131(do)003:722: pas 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi dkyil 'khor zhes byung
NK131(do)003:723: ba yin / phyis kyi brgyud 'dzin rnams kyang sngon
NK131(do)003:724: gyi tha tshig gis skyong zhing srung ba'i phyir mchod
NK131(do)003:725: bstod byed pa rgyal ba gong ma rnams kyi dgongs
NK131(do)003:726: pa ma nor ba yin pas skyon ci yang mi
NK131(do)003:727: ba yin / gnas / spyir chos skyong rnams kyang
NK131(do)003:728: gdul bya dang 'dul byed kyi ngo gang la ltos
NK131(do)003:729: nas ye shes 'jig rten gnyis rer gsungs pa yod
NK131(do)003:730: ba yin / gnas / de / mgon po yang
NK131(do)003:731: 'jig rten pa'i dus su dbang phyug chen po yin
NK131(do)003:732: ba yin / gnas / de / pa dang /
NK131(do)003:733: 'ga' zhig tu tshogs bdag dmar po dang mgon po
NK131(do)003:734: phyag bzhi pa dbang phyug gi bu bi na ya
NK131(do)003:735: ka ste log 'dren yin par gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)003:736: dpal ldan lha mo yang srin po mgrin bcu'i chung ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)003:737: gur mgon dang pe har rgyud gcig par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)003:738: yang pe har sku lnga ye shes pa'i dus su
NK131(do)003:739: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i rnam 'phrul du'ang gsungs pa sogs
NK131(do)003:740: cir yang bsgyur du btub pas mtha' gcig tu de
NK131(do)003:741: rnams la pho 'dre mo 'dre zhes smra bar mi
NK131(do)003:742: rigs te / de rnams la mchod pa byas tshad bsod nams dman pa yin na /
NK131(do)003:743: rgyal ba gong ma rtsod bral de rnams kyis bsten cing mchod pa ma 'os pa yin nam /
NK131(do)003:744: yang na khyed nyid 'khrul par nges so //
NK131(do)003:745: phyis kyi shugs ldan pa dang /
NK131(do)003:746: zhang pan du grags pa sogs ni rgyal ba de
NK131(do)003:747: dag gi dam 'og tu chud pa lta ci de
NK131(do)003:748: dag gi mtshan tsam grags pa'ang med pa'i 'dre gsar
NK131(do)003:749: byung yin pas / sde dgon che che mo thams
NK131(do)003:750: cad la gnod pa 'ba' zhig btang nas sdod du
NK131(do)003:751: ma ster nas skyabs su 'dzin dgos byung ba'i rigs
NK131(do)003:752: can de 'dra rnying ma phyogs su ye med de
NK131(do)003:753: byung yin pas / / thams cad mkhyen pa rgyal ba blo bzang rgya mtshos /
NK131(do)003:754: sngon byung gdon tshogs zad pa med pa'i steng /
NK131(do)003:755: gsar skyes dam sri dbyar mtsho ltar 'phel ba'i //
NK131(do)003:756: dus 'dir sngags 'chang ral khur ldan rnams kyis //
NK131(do)003:757: drag sngags dmod pa'i mtshon char 'bebs par bskul //
NK131(do)003:758: zhes rnying ma'i sngags 'chang rnams la de dag 'dul bar gsung gis bskul ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:759: rgyal po dang dam sri gsar skyes stobs che che
NK131(do)003:760: thams cad la glo snying brang gsum gyi gtad yul
NK131(do)003:761: bla ma dang dkon mchog las lhag par blta zhing
NK131(do)003:763: dar zab gang bzang gtubs nas ru mtshon dang zhag pa beng phod khrab gdon dor ma sogs bcos /
NK131(do)003:764: gser dngul las mda' mdung ral gri sa ga thag
NK131(do)003:765: sogs rngam rngam rdzig rdzig mang po byas nas dpyangs
NK131(do)003:766: / gcan gzan dang khyi rgod yan gyi phyi rten btsugs /
NK131(do)003:767: lha tho dmar po re dang shing sdong la sa dmar yan chad byug /
NK131(do)003:768: rkyal pa dbus kyis bkang nas kha mig bris pa
NK131(do)003:769: yan chad kyis 'dre de dag gnas rten 'cha' ba'i
NK131(do)003:770: re ba byed kyin 'dug pa la dpag na khyed
NK131(do)003:771: rang gis gong du bris pa'i slob dpon chen po'i
NK131(do)003:772: lung bstan las / lha ru 'dre srin 'gong po mchod //
NK131(do)003:773: dus ngan de rnams byung ba dang //
NK131(do)003:776: dus ngan snyigs ma'i sems can rnams //
NK131(do)003:777: phra ba yi dam lha ltar mchod //
NK131(do)003:778: zhes pa'i don thog tu babs pa khyed rang gsungs
NK131(do)003:779: pa ltar ba rkun gang yin rkang pa bskums nas
NK131(do)003:780: gnong rang thog tu blangs pa ngo mtshar che /
NK131(do)003:781: rnying ma pa tshos gtor ma khyi so tsam re dang /
NK131(do)003:782: skyems phud kong bu re mchod pa las de tsam gyi kha stabs kyang med la /
NK131(do)003:783: de 'dra byed pa'i srol yang med do //
NK131(do)003:784: khyed kyis lha 'dre de rnams mchod pas bsod nams
NK131(do)003:785: zad pa'i rgyur khas blangs pa ltar na dam sri
NK131(do)003:786: de dag mchod pa bsod nams dman pa'i rgyur 'gro
NK131(do)003:787: srid / gzhan chos skyong rnams la mchod bstod byas
NK131(do)003:788: pa der 'gyur na bod ljongs su dpal sa skya
NK131(do)003:789: srid / gong 'og / bkra shis lhun po /
NK131(do)003:793: 'bri stag kar 'brug sogs kyis mtshon pa ris su
NK131(do)003:794: ma chad pa'i dge 'dun gyi sde bstan pa 'dzin
NK131(do)003:795: pa'i gtso bo thams cad rang rang gi chos skyong
NK131(do)003:796: re dang bstan srung re la mchod bstod mi byed
NK131(do)003:798: de rnams la basngagasa pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)003:799: me phar la bus na sma ra tshul tshig pa 'dra'o //
NK131(do)003:800: des na tshe phyi ma rgyang du 'phangs nas 'di
NK131(do)003:801: pa'i ched kho nar 'jig rten gyi lha 'dre mthu
NK131(do)003:802: bo che bsten zhing dkon mchog la mchod pa byed
NK131(do)003:803: pa'i don du 'dre de dag la glo snying brang
NK131(do)003:804: gsum gtod nas mthu gtad byad gsum byed pa zhig
NK131(do)003:805: mchis na gong gi lung de'i don thog tu babs
NK131(do)003:806: shing / 'di phyi gtan brlag gi rgyur 'gyur bas
NK131(do)003:807: rang gzhan su la 'dug kyang dgag bya yin par
NK131(do)003:810: nged dga' ldan pa'i gral nas tshul mthun byed mi
NK131(do)003:811: 'dod pa 'ga' re slob dpon pad+ma'i rjes su 'brang
NK131(do)003:812: ba dang zhal gzigs dang lung bstan byung skad byed
NK131(do)003:815: dge ldan pa'i gral du bzhugs pa la slob dpon
NK131(do)003:816: rin po che'i dag snang zhal gzigs lung bstan byung
NK131(do)003:817: bas tshul min byed pa yin na phung tshabs che
NK131(do)003:818: ste / thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun rgya mtshos
NK131(do)003:819: dag snang la zhing khams thams cad du byon zhing
NK131(do)003:820: mthar rnga yab pad+ma 'od kyi pho brang chen por
NK131(do)003:821: gu ru rin po che'i drung du jo bo rje
NK131(do)003:822: sogs bzhugs 'dug par zhu gnang mang po mdzad nas
NK131(do)003:823: da khyod bod du 'gro ba'i don la song gsungs
NK131(do)003:824: nas skyes pa dmar po go khrab can zhig skyel
NK131(do)003:825: bar btang nas khang gsar gong du sleb par gsungs
NK131(do)003:826: pa rje bsod nams rgya mtsho yin zhing rgyal ba
NK131(do)003:827: de nyid kyang slob dpon rin po che'i zhal mjal
NK131(do)003:829: rgyal ba lnga pa chen po la dus rtag tu
NK131(do)003:830: slob dpon 'bral med du bzhugs pa gsang ba'i rnam
NK131(do)003:831: thar dag snang rgya can skor rnams su gsal ba
NK131(do)003:832: ltar dang / de bzhin du 'phags pa lha rim byon dang /
NK131(do)003:833: rgyal sras blo bzang bstan 'dzin sogs rim byon /
NK131(do)003:834: sems dpa' rin po che gong 'og /
NK131(do)003:835: chab mdo rje drung dge 'dun bkra shis skye ba gong 'og thams cad /
NK131(do)003:836: de mo rin po che skye phreng thams cad la
NK131(do)003:837: slob dpon gyi zhal gzigs lung bstan ma byung ba
NK131(do)003:838: med cing / de bzhin du stong skor chos rje bsod nams rgya mtsho skye phreng du ma /
NK131(do)003:839: chab mdo zhi ba bzang po gong 'og /
NK131(do)003:840: stag phu rin po che blo bzang chos kyi dbang
NK131(do)003:841: phyug sogs dge lugs kyi bstan 'dzin che phra smos
NK131(do)003:842: kyis mi lang ba zhig la slob dpon dag snang
NK131(do)003:843: la mjal ba byung 'dug pas de thams cad tshul
NK131(do)003:844: min byed 'dod dang tshad ldan min par 'dod na
NK131(do)003:845: khyod kyis tshul bzang can dang tshad ldan gyi chos
NK131(do)003:846: lugs gzhan zhig rnyed par dka' snyam mo //
NK131(do)003:847: gzhan grub mtha' ris med kyi mkhas grub dam pa
NK131(do)003:848: rnams la o rgyan rin po che'i dag snang lung
NK131(do)003:849: bstan gyi chos skor mtha' yas par bzhugs pa rnams
NK131(do)003:850: su ma zad rgya gar gyi grub chen zhi ba
NK131(do)003:851: sbas pa dang / pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai /
NK131(do)003:852: pha dam pa sogs slob dpon mjal nas dbang gdams
NK131(do)003:853: ngag gnang bar gsungs pa sogs smos kyis mi lang
NK131(do)003:854: zhing 'dir bri bar mi nus so //
NK131(do)003:856: gzhan yang cho ga ma tshang ba lhad zhugs pa dang /
NK131(do)003:857: log sgrub log 'tsho lnga sgrub pa la brtson zhing /
NK131(do)003:859: bu med 'dzem med du spyod pa sogs /
NK131(do)003:860: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang mi mthun par byed kyang /
NK131(do)003:861: rang gi nyes skyon yin mi zer ba ma zad /
NK131(do)003:862: slob dpon gyi lugs srol yin skad dang /
NK131(do)003:863: slob dpon gyi rjes 'brangs yin zer ba'i sa steng
NK131(do)003:864: khyab pa lta bur 'dug pa'i shes ldan rnams kyi
NK131(do)003:865: / bltas na de rnams kyis slob dpon pad+ma dgra
NK131(do)003:866: yi dang mar bzung nas dma' phang ci thub byed
NK131(do)003:867: pa las gzhan gang yang mthong rgyu med /
NK131(do)003:868: ngan pa de 'dra slob dpon gyi lugs ga la yin /
NK131(do)003:870: cho ga ma tshang zhing lhad zhugs pa gang yin
NK131(do)003:871: bkod rigs pa la 'god rgyu ci yang ma byung
NK131(do)003:872: 'dug pas smyon ham du grub bo //
NK131(do)003:873: bud med dang chang la spyod pa'ang gnang bkag gi
NK131(do)003:874: mtshams ma phyed par bab chol du smras pa tsam
NK131(do)003:875: ste / 'o na rgyud sde rnams su dbang gsum pa dang /
NK131(do)003:876: de las byung ba'i lhan skyes kyi ye shes dang /
NK131(do)003:877: pho nya'i lam rab 'byams gsungs pa thams cad kyi dgos pa ci zhig /
NK131(do)003:878: skyo 'dul 'dzin bya bas sngags kyi spyod pa la ma mgu bas /
NK131(do)003:879: ra lo rdo rje grags kyis /
NK131(do)003:880: dam nyams sgrol ba sngags kyi dam tshig yin //
NK131(do)003:881: bud med sbyor ba sngags kyi spyod pa yin //
NK131(do)003:882: sha chang bza' ba sngags kyi tshogs 'khor yin //
NK131(do)003:883: kho bos de ltar shes pas gnas skabs na //
NK131(do)003:884: 'dul 'dzin dge slong dag dang khyad par med //
NK131(do)003:885: de bas dam nyams log lta can khyod kyang //
NK131(do)003:886: zhag bdun nangs par gshegs su gsol bar bya //
NK131(do)003:887: zhes gsungs pas kyang gsal lo //
NK131(do)003:888: des na sbyor sgrol sngags kyi spyod par gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:889: min na gzhan gang la ngos 'dzin bsam par bya
NK131(do)003:890: ste / rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi rgyud rtogs pa bdun pa las /
NK131(do)003:891: nya yi sha dang chang dang bcas par /
NK131(do)003:893: bud med thams cad dbang du 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)003:895: bud med dbang du bya bar 'dod na /
NK131(do)003:897: ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar du mi 'dral lo //
NK131(do)003:898: zhes las rgya dbang du sdud pa'i skor shin tu mang po rgyud rnams su gsungs shing /
NK131(do)003:900: sangs rgyas rnams ni mnyes bya dang //
NK131(do)003:901: dam tshig rnams ni srung ba dang //
NK131(do)003:902: sngags rig pas ni sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK131(do)003:903: gzhan gyi bud med bstan par bya //
NK131(do)003:904: zhes sogs mtha' yas par gsungs shing de'ang lta ba
NK131(do)003:905: rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin la drod thob pa dag
NK131(do)003:906: gis sam / yang na dad pa brtan cing sngags
NK131(do)003:907: la yid ches pa'i slob mas bla ma ye shes
NK131(do)003:908: gzigs pa dag gis ji ltar lung bstan pa ltar
NK131(do)003:909: spyod par gsungs pa yin na /
NK131(do)003:910: ci khyod kyis smras pa ltar na de rnams kyi dgos pa stong bar 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)003:911: de bas na rgyud sde thams cad la rgyab kyis phyogs par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)003:912: de bzhin du sha lnga dang /
NK131(do)003:914: chang ni bla med kyi dam rdzas khyad par can
NK131(do)003:915: du gsungs pa khyed rang gi gsang bde 'jigs gsum
NK131(do)003:916: gyi rgyud ma mthong na'ang mngon rtogs kha ton du
NK131(do)003:917: bya bzhin par nang mchod kyi tshig tsam la'ang rtog
NK131(do)003:920: chang med pa la ye shes ci //
NK131(do)003:921: chang ni ye shes skye ba'i rgyu //
NK131(do)003:924: chang dang sgron ma sangs rgyas rnams dang bzang po'i
NK131(do)003:925: yul rnams mtha' dag 'khor lo la ni bsten par
NK131(do)003:928: rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas 'dug ste //
NK131(do)003:929: thams cad zos shing kun spyad kyang //
NK131(do)003:931: snying rje ldan pas smos ci dgos //
NK131(do)003:932: zhes sogs lung mtha' yas shing 'phags yul gyi slob
NK131(do)003:933: dpon a b+ha ya lta bu'ang rdo rje phag mo
NK131(do)003:934: mi mo'i rnam pas ba lang gi sha khrag dang
NK131(do)003:935: bcas dmar rdzar re byin pa dang du ma blangs
NK131(do)003:936: pas sku tshe de la mchog gi dngos grub la
NK131(do)003:937: bar chad du gyur par gsungs pas shes nus so
NK131(do)003:938: // des na sngags spyod can thams cad mtha' gcig tu ngan par smra ba'ang mi legs shing /
NK131(do)003:939: gang zag gi rgyud tshod thams cad mkhyen pa'am 'phags
NK131(do)003:940: pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin pa las gzhan gyis
NK131(do)003:942: gzhan du snyigs ma'i dus 'dir gang zag tshad ldan
NK131(do)003:943: nyin skar lta bur dkon zhing dgos pa gang yang
NK131(do)003:944: mi shes bzhin du sngags kyi spyod pa la khungs
NK131(do)003:945: su byed pa'i tho co'i spyod pa bab chol du
NK131(do)003:946: byed pa rnams re zhig ma dag par byed dgos
NK131(do)003:947: pas khyed bden yang de lta bu rnying ma gcig
NK131(do)003:949: rang gzhan thams cad la mtha' med par 'dug pas
NK131(do)003:950: bkag pas mi lang zhing sus su dgag /'dod pa
NK131(do)003:951: dang 'jigs skyob kyi phyir bstan pa la zhugs nas
NK131(do)003:952: gos ngur smriig bgos bzhin du kla klo'i sde rnams
NK131(do)003:953: dang spyod yul gcig tu gnas shing myos byed dang
NK131(do)003:954: tha ma kha la bag med du spyod pa dang
NK131(do)003:955: 'phral gyi bcas pa phra mo la 'jom pa ltar
NK131(do)003:956: snang gi gom pa lhod cing pham ltung ches che
NK131(do)003:957: ba rnams la mchongs rgyangs gnang ba'i deng dus kyi
NK131(do)003:958: rab byung gi gzugs brnyan tshong 'dus su sems can
NK131(do)003:959: lus stobs che ba la nom nyug byed cing rtags
NK131(do)003:960: kyis spras nas gzhan la gsod du bcug nas dmar
NK131(do)003:962: tshong khe spogs la yi dam du byed /
NK131(do)003:963: g.yo sgyus gzhan mgo skor ba dang /
NK131(do)003:964: so nam dang dmag las sogs khyim pa'i spyod pa la 'jug pa mang zhing /
NK131(do)003:965: bstan pa'i don du mi rta bsad na nyes pa med ces smra ba'ang thos na /
NK131(do)003:966: dge 'dun gyis nyan bshad sgom pa dang bslab pa
NK131(do)003:967: gsum gyi bstan pa 'dzin pa las dmag 'khrugs kyis
NK131(do)003:969: bla ma dge bshes dge slong gi dge 'dun 'ga' zhig dmag las la 'jug cing dmag bskul ba /
NK131(do)003:971: grong khyer 'joms shing dge 'dun gyis dge 'dun la
NK131(do)003:972: dmag gi las byed cing dkon mchog gsum la bsti
NK131(do)003:973: stang ma yin pa'i las la 'jug pa rgyal ba'i
NK131(do)003:974: bstan pa la kla klo'i spyod tshul gyis skabs btsam
NK131(do)003:975: pa la tsham tshom med par 'jug par mthong ste
NK131(do)003:976: / mdzod las dmag la sogs pa don gcig phyir //
NK131(do)003:977: thams cad byed pa po bzhin ldan //
NK131(do)003:978: zhes pa 'di la sde snod smra ba rnams kyis cung zad bsam dgos pa 'dra /
NK131(do)003:979: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis gzhan la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)003:980: gdug can re'i 'tsho ba'i rgyun bcad pa la'ang ltung
NK131(do)003:981: ba'i gzugs brnyan du gsungs na rang phyogs bsrung phyir
NK131(do)003:982: gzhan sde 'joms pa rnams 'jig rten pa'i spyod yul
NK131(do)003:983: las khyad zhugs pa ci yang med do //
NK131(do)003:984: spyod tshul de lta bu la zhugs pa rnams kyis
NK131(do)003:985: slob dpon pad+ma'i lugs srol dang rjes 'jug tu khas
NK131(do)003:987: de yod na slob dpon pad+mas khag bkal na tshogs par 'dug /
NK131(do)003:988: med na 'di rnams kyis rgyal ba thub pa'i dbang
NK131(do)003:989: po byang sems nyan rang bcas pa dang so so'i
NK131(do)003:991: rgyal ba'i sde snod gsum gyi bstan pa la dgra
NK131(do)003:992: yi dngas mar bzung nas shin tu sma phab cing
NK131(do)003:993: rang gzhan thams cad kyi gtan bde 'joms pa'i bya
NK131(do)003:994: ba rlabs po cher mi 'gyur ram shes ldan rnams
NK131(do)003:997: ngan sngags byed pa'i gzhan bsod nams zad pa'i tshe
NK131(do)003:998: cung zad gnod thub kyang bsod nams zad dus ngan
NK131(do)003:999: sngags byas kyang mi dgos kho rang shugs kyi nyams
NK131(do)003:1000: nas 'gro / bsod nams 'bar ba la ni ci
NK131(do)003:1001: yang mi gnod par ma zad pa'i tshe cung zad
NK131(do)003:1002: rang nyid 'di phyi kun tu 'phong bar 'gyur ba'i
NK131(do)003:1003: de dag la bla ma dang skyabs gnas re ltos
NK131(do)003:1004: bca' ba ni las ngan pa'i dbang gi yin nam
NK131(do)003:1005: nas 'gro / snyam / zhes brjod bya thabs rdugs 'di 'dra bris so //
NK131(do)003:1006: de ltar na rdo rje 'chang gis rgyud sde rnams
NK131(do)003:1007: su mngon spyod kyi las rab 'byams shig gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:1008: rnams la dgos pa ma mchis te /
NK131(do)003:1009: gdul bya gdug pa can de'i bsod nams 'phel 'grib
NK131(do)003:1010: la ltos dgos par grub cing bsod nams che ba
NK131(do)003:1011: la ci yang mi thub par ma zad rang nyid
NK131(do)003:1012: phung bar khas blangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:1013: de ni rang nyid la sngags kyi nus pas ma gos pa'i thabs rdugs kyi gtam shor ba ste /
NK131(do)003:1014: pha rol po bsod nams che ba la gnod par
NK131(do)003:1015: ma nus na bsod nams zad pa zhig la mngon
NK131(do)003:1017: slob dpon mar me mdzad bzang pos sin+du'i yul gyi
NK131(do)003:1018: mu stegs la mos pa'i rgyal po b+h+au sh+aan zhes
NK131(do)003:1019: bya ba yo byad dang bcas thal bar mdzad pa
NK131(do)003:1020: dang / nub phyogs ma la ba'i yul gyi rgyal
NK131(do)003:1021: po chen po lha khyab 'jug gis mngon sum du
NK131(do)003:1022: dngos grub sbyin par byed pa zhig kyang slob dpon
NK131(do)003:1023: gyis ras la bris pa'i ling+ga phyed mar bshags pas
NK131(do)003:1024: rgyal po lus tshal par gas te shi ba sogs
NK131(do)003:1025: dang / / bsod nams shin tu che ba rnams
NK131(do)003:1026: kyang sngags kyi mthus gzhom par mdzad pa'i lo rgyus
NK131(do)003:1027: dang / / mang zhing / bod kyi ljongs 'dir
NK131(do)003:1028: yang so zur gnubs gsum he ru ka mi gzugs
NK131(do)003:1029: su byon pa rnams kyis bsad gso gnyis ka mdzad
NK131(do)003:1030: pa'i rnam thar mang bar yod cing /
NK131(do)003:1031: tsha ko dbon po ngag dbang grags pas 'jigs byed
NK131(do)003:1032: kyi 'khrul 'khor la brten nas bon po mang po
NK131(do)003:1033: bsgral ba dang / ra lo chen po sogs mthu
NK131(do)003:1034: chen rnams kyi lo rgyus la ltos shig dang de
NK131(do)003:1035: rnams la skyabs dang re ltos bca' ba las ngan
NK131(do)003:1036: yin na khyod rang rnams kyang rdo rje 'jigs byed
NK131(do)003:1037: rwa lugs zhes rtsis cher byed pa'i chos dang bla
NK131(do)003:1038: ma gnyis ka 'dor dgos par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)003:1039: rwa lo rdo rje grags ni /
NK131(do)003:1040: gnyan lo ts+aa sogs rang mnyam gyi lo ts+aa ba
NK131(do)003:1041: bcu gsum mar pa'i sras dar ma mdo sde sogs
NK131(do)003:1042: sa thob sems dpa' bcu drug bkrongs mkhan de yin
NK131(do)003:1043: pas so // der ma zad grub pa'i slob dpon kun dga' snying po'i gsung pas /
NK131(do)003:1044: gsang sngags kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i nang na /
NK131(do)003:1045: gdug la rtag tu byams ldan par //
NK131(do)003:1046: byed pa de ni bcu par 'dod //
NK131(do)003:1047: ces bya ba gcig mi gda' 'am /
NK131(do)003:1048: gdug pa can la snying nye bar byas na rtsa ltung yin par bshad /
NK131(do)003:1049: de'i shugs las mngon spyod ma byas na nyes pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1050: byas na phan yon 'byung zer ba gcig yong ba yin /
NK131(do)003:1051: mi nag pa chos la sol phye las gnag pa /
NK131(do)003:1052: dbang 'dra yod pas dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang smad pa rnams /
NK131(do)003:1053: mngon spyod kyi yul yin pa lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK131(do)003:1054: chos pa'am dge bshes su bardzu ba /
NK131(do)003:1055: bstan pa dang sems can la gnod pa rang byed pa 'di kun kyang /
NK131(do)003:1056: bsgral bar bya ba'i yul yin te /
NK131(do)003:1057: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po pan+di ta d+harma rak+shi tas kyang /
NK131(do)003:1058: bzang po lta bur kun gyis bcos na yang //
NK131(do)003:1059: log lta'i nags su bdag lta 'khrugs pa yis //
NK131(do)003:1060: stag mo bu zan lta bur 'jigs pa de //
NK131(do)003:1061: bka' sdod srung ma rnams kyis bsgral bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1062: ngur smrig gos can zhi dul mdzes gyur kyang //
NK131(do)003:1063: byi la bzhin du bsam pa ma rungs pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1064: dam pa'i gzugs brnyan gso ru med pa de //
NK131(do)003:1065: ma mo rnams kyi kha ru gdams bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1066: khri phrag dgu yi gtso bor 'dug gyur kyang //
NK131(do)003:1067: khyab 'jug bzhin du rang rgyud ma thul ba'i //
NK131(do)003:1068: chags sdang 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro ba de //
NK131(do)003:1069: gshin rje gshed kyi zhal du gdab bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1070: khyim nas byung zhing bstan pa'i sgor zhugs kyang //
NK131(do)003:1071: khyim pa bzhin du bya ba mtha' yas shing //
NK131(do)003:1072: spang blang thams cad khyad du gsod pa de //
NK131(do)003:1073: drang srong rnams kyis dmod pas gdams bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1074: rtags dang ldan yang tshul khrims mi bsrung zhing //
NK131(do)003:1075: 'dod pa'i las la snang ba 'byams gyur nas //
NK131(do)003:1076: dam pa rnams la sgro skur 'debs pa de //
NK131(do)003:1077: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis pha rol bsgral bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1078: rnyed pa'i ched du dam pa'i gzugs bzung nas //
NK131(do)003:1079: khyi phag bzhin du 'dod yon 'byol nyog spyod //
NK131(do)003:1080: sngags su khas blangs thams cad bslu ba de //
NK131(do)003:1081: rdo rje 'dzin pas thab tu gzhug bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1082: theg chen skad du las 'bras khyad gsod cing //
NK131(do)003:1083: stong pa'i rbad kyis 'khor tshogs bslu ba yis //
NK131(do)003:1084: 'gong po bzhin du sku ru bardzu ba de //
NK131(do)003:1085: dam tshig can gyis sngags kyis bsod bya yin //
NK131(do)003:1086: 'di ltar so sor thar pa phar zhog gi //
NK131(do)003:1087: rang nyid ngan 'gro chen por 'gro dgos kyang //
NK131(do)003:1088: bstan pa 'jigs pa'i dgra bgegs mi sgrol re //
NK131(do)003:1089: dam nyams pha rol dgra bgegs bsgral bar bya //
NK131(do)003:1090: zhes 'byung ba 'di la brtags na skye bo gzhan lta ci smos /
NK131(do)003:1091: deng sang bstan pa la zhugs pa'i gzugs brnyan phal
NK131(do)003:1092: che ba mngon spyod kyi yul las ma 'das pas
NK131(do)003:1093: rang rgyud bag yod byed dgos par rigs so //
NK131(do)003:1094: gzhung 'di byang chub sems dpa'i blo sbyong gi gzhung yin /
NK131(do)003:1098: khyed rang rnams kyis kha 'dzin du byed pa'i byang
NK131(do)003:1099: chub sems kyi mnga' bdag bshes gnyen bka' gdams pa
NK131(do)003:1100: rnams kyis rtsis su mdzad pa yin pas /
NK131(do)003:1101: mngon spyod dang chub chub kyi sems 'gal mi 'gal bsam mno thongs /
NK131(do)003:1102: gal te rdo rje slob dpon rnams kyis mngon spyod byar mi rung na /
NK131(do)003:1103: rgyud sde bzhi po thams cad nas bsad skrod dbye
NK131(do)003:1104: ba rmongs rengs phur gdab kyi las mtha' yas pa
NK131(do)003:1105: zhig gsungs 'dug pa thams cad dgos med du thal
NK131(do)003:1107: zhes gsungs pa de tsam gyis kyang shes par nus
NK131(do)003:1108: pas rang nyid sngags la skal ba chad cing thos
NK131(do)003:1109: pa phyogs 'go tsam yang med pa'i nang rtags phyi
NK131(do)003:1110: rol du ngom pa rgod bro'o //
NK131(do)003:1113: rgyud khung ma nas gsungs pa'i drag las rnams don gtan nas mi 'dra ste /
NK131(do)003:1114: ngan sngags rnams ni chos log yin pa'i de byed
NK131(do)003:1115: pa ni 'di phyi kun tu 'phong bar 'gyur zhing
NK131(do)003:1116: / de sgrub pa po rnams grib can yin pa'i
NK131(do)003:1117: de dag dang 'grogs 'brel byed na nyams grib phog
NK131(do)003:1118: rgyud nas gsungs pa'i drag las rnams tshul bzhin byed
NK131(do)003:1119: na rang gzhan thams cad la gtan du phan par
NK131(do)003:1120: 'gyur ba rdo rje 'chang rang nyid kyis gsungs /
NK131(do)003:1122: de ni ngan sngags zhes ming tsam las ngan pa
NK131(do)003:1123: zhig yin du yod bsams shing don ma rtogs pas
NK131(do)003:1124: 'khrul te / rgyal bas rgyud sde rnams su mngon
NK131(do)003:1125: spyod kyi las bsad bskrad dbye rmongs pa rengs pa
NK131(do)003:1126: smyo lkugs mnan sregs sogs grangs med cig bka' stsal
NK131(do)003:1128: sngags dang ting nge 'dzin la brten nas bya bar
NK131(do)003:1129: gsungs pas sngags bzla ba gtso bor ston pa la
NK131(do)003:1130: dgongs shing / de'ang byang chub sems kyis zin zhing thabs la ma rmongs pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1131: shes rab khyad par can dang 'brel pa las rnam
NK131(do)003:1132: pa ngan thabs 'ba' zhig yin pas ngan sngags sam
NK131(do)003:1133: mngon spyod kyi las zhes bya ste /
NK131(do)003:1135: me yi dkyil 'khor dbus gnas par //
NK131(do)003:1136: dgra bo rnams ni sreg par sgom //
NK131(do)003:1137: sangs rgyas kun la gnod byed par //
NK131(do)003:1138: bsams nas rnal 'byor sbyar bar bya //
NK131(do)003:1141: zhes pa 'di'i stongs kyi sems dang las kyi sbyor
NK131(do)003:1142: ba de dag ngan thabs min na bzang thabs su
NK131(do)003:1143: 'gyur ram / 'jigs byed rtogs bdun gyi 'khor lo'i man ngag las /
NK131(do)003:1144: rang gi lte bar 'khor lo phyi brgyad nang brgyad /
NK131(do)003:1146: lte bar rlung gi dkyil 'khor de'i steng du me'i dkyil 'khor /
NK131(do)003:1148: dgra bgegs 'di zhes bya ba'i ming de'i steng du
NK131(do)003:1149: ya yig gshin rje gshed kyi ngo bos mnan par
NK131(do)003:1151: dgra'i ming dang steng gi ya yig la sems gtad cing /
NK131(do)003:1152: ya m+aan+ta ka sha t+aum m+aa ra ya h'u phata h+r+aihsh+ti sogs /
NK131(do)003:1153: yig 'bru rnams las pho nya drag gtum mtshon cha
NK131(do)003:1154: thogs pas dgra bgegs kyi lus dum bur gtubs pa
NK131(do)003:1156: dug dang nad kyis char phab ste lus rul zhing
NK131(do)003:1157: myog par byed pa sogs sngags brgya tsam gyi ring
NK131(do)003:1158: thun gyi tha mar dmigs pa de lta bu bya'o
NK131(do)003:1162: rtsa sngags rnams la sha trum a kar+sha ya dza
NK131(do)003:1163: dza sbyar ba zla zhing yig 'bru rnams las khro
NK131(do)003:1164: bo dpag tu med pa 'phros dgra bgegs kyi lus
NK131(do)003:1165: mtshon cha sna tshogs pas gtubs te gsol bar bsam
NK131(do)003:1166: pa dang / las kyi gshin rje dang srin po
NK131(do)003:1167: mkha' 'gro ma dang ma mo la sogs 'jig rten
NK131(do)003:1168: pa'i lha tshogs spros nas mtshon cha /
NK131(do)003:1170: sbrul gdug pa can spros te sha rus za bar bsam /
NK131(do)003:1172: nad kyi char pa babs te tshar bcad par bsam /
NK131(do)003:1173: sha khrag kyang mes bsregs shing thal ba rnams kyang rlung gis khyer bar bsams la /
NK131(do)003:1176: snying po dang nye snying rnams la gnod byed m+aa ra ya phata btags la bazla'o //
NK131(do)003:1177: zhes gsungs pa 'di rnams ngan sngags bzla zhing bsam
NK131(do)003:1178: ngan bsgom pa min na bzang sngags dang bsam bzang
NK131(do)003:1180: rang gis tshad mar 'dod cing yid ma snying por
NK131(do)003:1181: byed rgyu'i rgyud dang sgrub thabs su ci 'dra yod
NK131(do)003:1182: ma mthong bar gzhan gyi lugs de ngan pa zhig
NK131(do)003:1183: yin yod snyam nas kha nas gang thon byas pas
NK131(do)003:1184: rang skyon rang gis brtol bas rjes su yi rang
NK131(do)003:1185: ngo // des na rgyud du gsungs pa'i drag las
NK131(do)003:1186: dang ngan sngags ngo bo gcig pa nyid las gzhan
NK131(do)003:1187: du drags las ma yin pa'i ngan sngags zhig dang
NK131(do)003:1188: de ma yin pa'i drag las zur pa ci 'dra
NK131(do)003:1189: zhig yod ston par gyis shig /
NK131(do)003:1190: yang mthu gtad mnan gsum rgyud nas ma gsungs bsam
NK131(do)003:1191: pa zhig byung 'dug pa don ma shes pa'i blun
NK131(do)003:1193: mnan pa ni rengs par byed pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1194: gtad ni bsad pa sogs kyis las de rnams sde
NK131(do)003:1195: brgyad mthu bo che rnams la byed du bcug pa
NK131(do)003:1196: tsam yin pas so sor ma 'khrul cig /
NK131(do)003:1197: mthu zhes pa nus pa dang don gcig pa tsam
NK131(do)003:1198: yang ma go nas rgyud nas ma gsungs bsams 'dug
NK131(do)003:1200: yang slob dpon pad+ma'i gter chos rnams su drag las
NK131(do)003:1201: sna tshogs rab 'byams gsungs pa rnams la bsams nas
NK131(do)003:1202: ngan sngags dang drag lasatha dad du smras pa yin
NK131(do)003:1203: na / de rnams kyang thabs shes khyad par can
NK131(do)003:1204: gyis zin pas gong du brjod pa dang gcig cing
NK131(do)003:1205: na / / de dag gis ma zin pa'i ngan thabs kho na ni phyi rol pa ste /
NK131(do)003:1206: dbang phyug dang khyab 'jug gi rjes 'brangs dang kla
NK131(do)003:1207: klo sogs la grags pa yod srid kyang de la
NK131(do)003:1208: spyod pa'i gang zag ni 'dir smos ma dgos so
NK131(do)003:1209: // gzhan yang phyag na pad+mo ngur smrig 'chang ba rgyal dbang lnga pa chen pos /
NK131(do)003:1210: stong bshad khar 'byams lo pan brgyud chos rgod //
NK131(do)003:1211: gshog rgyas gdugs ltar phub pa ma yin par //
NK131(do)003:1212: rgya khra gzan 'jug drang srong dmod pa'i mchus //
NK131(do)003:1213: lag rjes rim byung gsung sgrogs yon gyi dpe //
NK131(do)003:1214: zhes gsar ma phyogs su grags pa'i drag las rnams
NK131(do)003:1215: cung zad g.yel bar gyur pa la thugs ma rang
NK131(do)003:1216: nas gter ma'i man ngag rnams thugs nyams su bzhes
NK131(do)003:1217: shing dus skabs der be ri rgyal po dang sgar
NK131(do)003:1218: gtsang mchod yon sogs sku dbang btsan pas dge lugs
NK131(do)003:1219: pa rnams mdzad dkar gyur pa rgyal dbang thams cad
NK131(do)003:1220: mkhyen pas rnying ma'i bla ma zur chen chos dbyings
NK131(do)003:1221: rang grol / khra tshang pa blo mchog rdo rje /
NK131(do)003:1222: chos rgyal gter bdag gling pa sogs mang du bsten
NK131(do)003:1223: nas bka' gter snyan brgyud kyi chos bka' bod du
NK131(do)003:1224: grags pa thams cad gsan cing thugs nyams su bzhes
NK131(do)003:1225: shing khyad par drag po mngon spyod kyi las rab
NK131(do)003:1226: 'byams la brten nas be ri rgyal po dang gtsang
NK131(do)003:1227: pa rgyal po sogs rang bstan la 'tshe ba mang
NK131(do)003:1228: zhig ming gi lhag mar tshar bcad nas ri bo
NK131(do)003:1229: dge ldan pa'i chos srid kyis yangs pa'i sa chen
NK131(do)003:1230: po khyab par mdzad pa zhal gyis bzhes pa rnam
NK131(do)003:1231: thar chen mor gsal ba ltar yin te rgyal ba
NK131(do)003:1233: rdzogs chen la brten 'chi med 'pho ba che //
NK131(do)003:1234: sgrub pa dkar po'i chos kyi bde skyid grong //
NK131(do)003:1235: srung byed nag po mthu yi lcags ri 'di //
NK131(do)003:1236: ches cher snyigs ma'i dus 'dir lhag par mkho //
NK131(do)003:1238: gangs can phan bde'i srog 'phrog 'byung po'i gdon //
NK131(do)003:1239: de yis rgyud barlamasa mir bcas ma lus pa //
NK131(do)003:1240: dge ba'i gnam lcags brag ri'i thal mo'i bar //
NK131(do)003:1241: gang+g+aa'i klung gi rdul bzhin 'thag gyur cig /
NK131(do)003:1242: ces pa la sogs don dang mthun pa'i smon lam ched du brjod pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)003:1243: shes par 'dod na rgyal ba'i rnam thar gsung 'bum rnams la blta bar byos shig /
NK131(do)003:1244: bod kyi ljongs 'dir mtha' dmag dus 'khrugs sogs 'gag dog sar skyabs gnas o rgyan pad+ma la 'chol /
NK131(do)003:1245: blo gtad rnying ma'i chos la byed pa zhig sngon nas da lta'i bar byung 'dug cing /
NK131(do)003:1246: khyod kyis ngan sngags rnams chos log yin pas de
NK131(do)003:1247: sgrub pa 'di phyi kun tu phung bar 'gyur zhes
NK131(do)003:1248: pa dang / sgrub pa po rnams grib can yin pas de dang 'grogs na nyams grib phog /
NK131(do)003:1249: ces smras pa rnams gzas pa'i khar mi phog /
NK131(do)003:1250: ma gzas pa'i sna la phog nyan 'dug go //
NK131(do)003:1251: de bas na rang gi chos phugs dang skyabs yul la bsams nas bag yod par gyis shig /
NK131(do)003:1253: mu stegs byed bon po'i chos kha ton du byed
NK131(do)003:1254: pa 'ga' re ngag 'chal 'a ga' re tshig rtsubs
NK131(do)003:1255: su gsungs pa'i tshe phyi mar mi phan par ma
NK131(do)003:1256: zad gnod tshabs shin tu che /
NK131(do)003:1258: de dag spyir mu stegs byed la bsams na ci lta /
NK131(do)003:1259: ljongs 'dir mu stegs byed sngar byung ba mkhas pa sus kyang mi bzhed de /
NK131(do)003:1260: sa skya pan+di tas mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho'i gsung sdom gsum du drangs pa /
NK131(do)003:1261: rgyal po khyod kyi bod yul 'di //
NK131(do)003:1263: brtan ma bcu gnyis la gtad pas //
NK131(do)003:1265: zhes gsungs pas mkhas pa gzhan gang gis ma gzigs
NK131(do)003:1266: pa'i mu stegs byed kyi chos de dag gang yin
NK131(do)003:1267: khyed dri mkhan dang dri yul gnyis kas mthong 'dug
NK131(do)003:1268: pa de'i gzhung lugs nam byung /
NK131(do)003:1273: lar rnal 'byor rgyud kyi dbang gi dam tshig tu //
NK131(do)003:1274: mu stegs can la'ang smad mi bya //
NK131(do)003:1275: zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa 'di la tho phog tsam mi dgos sam /
NK131(do)003:1276: bon po'ang phyi bon zhes kla klo'i spyod pa can
NK131(do)003:1277: sngar bod du dar ba de ni slob dpon thugs
NK131(do)003:1278: rje can sogs chos rgyal lo pan rnams kyis gnas
NK131(do)003:1279: dbyung mdzad pa bod kyi mtha' rgya mtshams rnams su
NK131(do)003:1281: da lta bod na yod pa'i bon 'di rnams bon
NK131(do)003:1282: la dga' ba'i yul gyi mi dang mi ma yin
NK131(do)003:1283: rnams drang ba'i ched lha sngags cho ga sogs la
NK131(do)003:1284: tha snyad de ltar btags kyang ngo bo'i cha ni
NK131(do)003:1285: sangs rgyas pa'i chos dang mi mthun pa gang yang
NK131(do)003:1286: med de bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang mi
NK131(do)003:1287: 'gal zhing sdom pa gsum dang bskyed rdzogs sogs lam
NK131(do)003:1288: gyi rim pa dang spang bya'i nyon mongs /
NK131(do)003:1290: gzhi lam 'bras bu sku gsum gyi rnam gzhag bcas
NK131(do)003:1291: thams cad gcig par grub pa'i phyir thar lam med
NK131(do)003:1294: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK131(do)003:1295: dbang byas rnams g.yeng med yid can gyi bshad //
NK131(do)003:1296: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK131(do)003:1297: de ni drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bor blang //
NK131(do)003:1298: zhes gsungs pa'i don 'di ni rgyal ba'i bka' dang
NK131(do)003:1299: bstan bcos kyi don la dpyod pa'i shes rab rlabs
NK131(do)003:1300: po che rgyal ba byams pas stsal pa lags na
NK131(do)003:1301: 'di la rtog dpyod cung zad dgos par sems so
NK131(do)003:1302: // don la cung zad tsam yang mi rtog par
NK131(do)003:1303: ming tshig kho na'i rjes su hol rgyug byed cing
NK131(do)003:1304: lugs de ngan pa zhig yin yod bsams pa kho
NK131(do)003:1305: nas smras pa'i phyir snying pos dben pa kho na'o
NK131(do)003:1307: rgyal ba nyid kyis lung bstan pa'i klu sgrub thogs
NK131(do)003:1308: med gnyis dang rje tsong kha pa'i lugs srol la
NK131(do)003:1310: shing rta chen po de gnyis kyi lugs dang mi mthun pa'i chos rnams chos log tu bshad de /
NK131(do)003:1311: zhes red mda' pa'i gsung 'ga' re khungs su drangs so //
NK131(do)003:1312: rags pa tsam ni shing rta chen po de gnyis
NK131(do)003:1313: dang mi mthun pa'i bstan pa bod du byung ba
NK131(do)003:1314: med / zhib tu dpyad tshe de gnyis kyi lugs ma nor ba gang yin ngos 'dzin dka' ste /
NK131(do)003:1315: rgya bod kyi mkhas pa thams cad kyang de gnyis
NK131(do)003:1316: kyi lugs srol la mi mthun nas rtsod pa byung
NK131(do)003:1317: ba yin / dngos bstan du 'phags bod gnyis ka'i
NK131(do)003:1318: mkhas mi mkhas thams cad kyis shing rta chen po'i
NK131(do)003:1319: bzhed pa ni kho bo'i 'di kho na yin gyi
NK131(do)003:1321: 'ba' zhig gsungs pa yod de drang shan ji lta
NK131(do)003:1322: ba phye na 'phags pa rnams gnyis dngos su byon
NK131(do)003:1324: slob dpon 'di dag gi dgongs bzhi yang cung zad
NK131(do)003:1325: bshad du yod mod spros pas chog kyang 'dir yi
NK131(do)003:1326: ge mang zhing re zhig dgos pa cher ma mthong
NK131(do)003:1328: rang gi ma ngan song myong ba la bzod mi rigs na /
NK131(do)003:1329: rgyu sdig pa bsags pa la bzod ga la rig /
NK131(do)003:1330: chos log byed pa la khong khro byed mi nyan /
NK131(do)003:1333: ma ngan song du sdug bsngal ba bzod thabs med /
NK131(do)003:1334: de'i rgyu sdig pa bsags pa la'ang bzod pa mi sgom zer rgyu yin na /
NK131(do)003:1335: de la khong khro byed mi nyan /
NK131(do)003:1336: zhes pa bzod pa mi sgom pa dang khong khro mi nyan pa 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1337: yang ci mi snyam du mi bzhag par sdug bsngal
NK131(do)003:1338: de rgyu dang bcas sel ba'i thabs su 'bad dgos
NK131(do)003:1340: de la btang snyoms su mi bzhag zer dgos pa la bzod pa mi rigs zer ba 'gal zhing /
NK131(do)003:1341: bzod pa la sdug bsngal dang len /
NK131(do)003:1342: gnod pa la ci mi snyam pa /
NK131(do)003:1343: chos la nges 'byed mi bzod pa gsum du bshad pa'i rnam dbye ma go ba'o //
NK131(do)003:1344: yang khyed kyis chos log chos min yang yang brgya
NK131(do)003:1345: tshar stong tshar zlos pa gong du brjod pa de
NK131(do)003:1346: rnams su 'dod pa yin na ni rnam par dbye
NK131(do)003:1347: ba brjod zin pa der zad pas rdul phran gyi
NK131(do)003:1348: cha shas tsam yang chos log tu sgrub mi nus
NK131(do)003:1349: pas de tsam gyis lan gyis spros pa bcad do
NK131(do)003:1350: // lar khyed kyis dgag pa 'di'i klad gzhung mjug gsum thams cad kyi tshig dngos dang /
NK131(do)003:1351: de'i khungs su drangs pa rnams kyang gtso bor rang
NK131(do)003:1352: gi grub mtha' la mchog 'dzin gyi zhen pa dang
NK131(do)003:1353: / des gzhan la phrag dog gi rgyu byas nas
NK131(do)003:1354: rang nyid thos pa nyung zhing gsung rab thams cad
NK131(do)003:1355: la dpyod pa'i shes rab byis pa'i blo gros nar
NK131(do)003:1356: ma son pa'i nyams kho na las gzu bor gnas
NK131(do)003:1357: pa'i blos brtags na bzung du rung ba tshig gcig
NK131(do)003:1360: 'brom rin po ches chos la brten pa'i sdig pa'i
NK131(do)003:1361: gam na sdig pa gzhan chung chung yin gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:1362: ni / khyod rang la gsungs pa 'dra ste chos yin pa la min par smra ba dang /
NK131(do)003:1363: rang lta la mchog tu 'dzin cing gzhan gyi chos
NK131(do)003:1364: dang lta ba la zhe sdang ba'i gtam smra ba
NK131(do)003:1365: rnams chos la brten pa'i sdig par gsungs pa yin
NK131(do)003:1366: te khyod nyid kyi smra ba 'di lta bu'o //
NK131(do)003:1367: chos la gnod par byed pa rnams de la brten
NK131(do)003:1368: pa ma yin pa'i phyir 'di tsam yang ma go
NK131(do)003:1369: bas chos la dgag sgrub byed pa ngo mtshar che'o
NK131(do)003:1371: sgom chen sgom chung gi rnam dbye 'ga' re bris
NK131(do)003:1372: 'dug pa'ang blun gtam 'ba' zhig la dpyad par mi
NK131(do)003:1375: sems dang po nas sangs rgyas yin /
NK131(do)003:1376: sangs rgyas rang chas su yod kyang ngo ma shes pa yin zer ba dang /
NK131(do)003:1377: bla ma'i ngo sprod byas nas sems ngo 'phrod pa
NK131(do)003:1378: na sangs rgyas pa yin pa'i sems kyi ngo bo
NK131(do)003:1379: rang la bltas nas sdod pa'i chog gzhan gang yang
NK131(do)003:1381: yang lta ba thod rgal dang lam 'phrad gcod yin
NK131(do)003:1382: zer ba sogs sna tshogs zhig 'dug pa'i ji ltar
NK131(do)003:1384: sangs rgyas yin pa la rang gi rang ngo ma shes pa nyams rang tshang /
NK131(do)003:1385: rang chas su yod pa dang sgrub dgos pa yang 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1386: ci yang mi dgos zer ba dang sna tshogs byed pa yang 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1387: bla ma'i ngo sprod nas gsar du sangs rgyas mkhan
NK131(do)003:1388: de lus yin nam sems ni sngar sangs rgyas zin
NK131(do)003:1389: pa'i gsar du sangs rgyas pa 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1390: ji ltar byas kyang ltung bshags las lta ba log
NK131(do)003:1391: pa 'dzin par 'gyur ba zhes pa'i lta ngan mu
NK131(do)003:1392: stegs can dang mtshungs pa'i tha chad kyi lta ba
NK131(do)003:1393: zhig yin gsungs te rje btsun ngag dbang byams pa'i
NK131(do)003:1394: / bod kyi blos byas theg pa mthon po rnams //
