NK131(do)003:1395: mu stegs dang mtshungs rtags dngos yon tan kun //
NK131(do)003:1396: ye nas rdzogs pa sems can kun la yod //
NK131(do)003:1397: de nyid bla ma'i rang ngo sprod byas pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1398: ngo 'phrod tsam gyis sangs rgyas zhes brjod kyi //
NK131(do)003:1399: 'di las sa lam rim pa med ces smra //
NK131(do)003:1400: deng sang sa steng thams cad lug 'di khyab //
NK131(do)003:1401: rmongs dang le lo can la shin tu mkho //
NK131(do)003:1404: gsang sngags kyi lam ni shin tu rmongs pa dang
NK131(do)003:1405: dug lnga shas che ba le lo can grol bar
NK131(do)003:1406: byed pa'i lam ni yin te /
NK131(do)003:1408: gdol pa smyig ma mkhan la sogs mtshams med lnga ni byed pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1411: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)003:1412: zhes gsungs pa'i don 'di ji ltar drang /
NK131(do)003:1413: khyed cag drang don dang theg dman gyi lam la
NK131(do)003:1414: blo yi bag chags brtan che bas rgyal bas sems
NK131(do)003:1415: nyid sangs rgyas su bstan pa'i theg pa chen po'i
NK131(do)003:1416: gsang ba zab mo'i gnas rnams rna bar mi shor
NK131(do)003:1417: zhing shin tu skrag pa skye ba khag med de
NK131(do)003:1418: / de ltar ston pa de rnying ma gcig pu'i
NK131(do)003:1419: chos su bsams nas bkag par rlom pa ni rgya
NK131(do)003:1420: che ba'i gsung rab zab mo rnams mthong ma myong
NK131(do)003:1421: zhing thos pa chung bas rang mgo rang gis bcad
NK131(do)003:1423: dus kyi 'khor lo'i ye shes le'u las /
NK131(do)003:1424: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas yin te sangs rgyas
NK131(do)003:1425: chen po gzhan 'dir 'jig rten khams na yod ma
NK131(do)003:1426: yin zhes dang / dgyes pa rdo rje las /
NK131(do)003:1427: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK131(do)003:1429: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)003:1430: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK131(do)003:1431: de nyid bsal na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)003:1434: gzod nas sems can lhan cig skyes pa'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas so //
NK131(do)003:1436: de nyid sems can gyi rgyud la ji ltar bzhugs tshul yang /
NK131(do)003:1438: bum pa'i chu ni len par byed pa na yang nam mkha' 'gro ba min pa ji lta bar /
NK131(do)003:1439: mkha' khyab mkha' yi rdo rje can ni yul dang
NK131(do)003:1440: rnam par bral ba lus kyi dbus su de bzhin
NK131(do)003:1443: rang gi lus la sangs rgyas bzhugs //
NK131(do)003:1444: gzhan du gang na'ang sangs rgyas med //
NK131(do)003:1445: mi shes mun pas bsgribs pa rnams //
NK131(do)003:1446: lus las gzhan du sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK131(do)003:1449: lus can snying la gang gnas pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1450: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK131(do)003:1451: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK131(do)003:1452: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK131(do)003:1453: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK131(do)003:1455: rgyud kyi rgyal po kha sbyor thig le las /
NK131(do)003:1456: ye shes lnga yi ngo bo nyid //
NK131(do)003:1457: yungs kar sbom po'i cha tsam dag /
NK131(do)003:1458: de yi dbus na gnas pa'i lha //
NK131(do)003:1459: mi gsal gsal ba'i bdag nyid can //
NK131(do)003:1460: cha med mchog tu phra ba ste //
NK131(do)003:1461: thig le'i gzugs can yid kyi dngos //
NK131(do)003:1462: gzi brjid chen po'i 'od dang ldan //
NK131(do)003:1463: rtag tu snying gi dbus na gnas //
NK131(do)003:1465: bram ze chen po sa ra has /
NK131(do)003:1466: mkhas pa rnams ni bstan bcos 'chad pa yis //
NK131(do)003:1467: lus la ye shes yod pa ma rtogs so //
NK131(do)003:1470: 'dir sems can thams cad kyi snying gi nang na gnas pa ni ye shes so //
NK131(do)003:1473: 'gro ba kun la sangs rgyas mngon du bzhugs //
NK131(do)003:1476: kye rgyal ba'i sras dag de bzhin du de bzhin
NK131(do)003:1477: gshegs pa'i ye shes sems can thams cad kyi sems
NK131(do)003:1478: la rim gyis chud par gnas so //
NK131(do)003:1479: zhes sogs mtha' yas par gsungs pa'i phyir rdzogs chen
NK131(do)003:1480: gyi gzhung rnams su de dang mthun pa shin tu
NK131(do)003:1481: gsal zhing rgyas par gsungs pa la bsams nas sangs
NK131(do)003:1482: rgyas kyi bka' zab mo'i mdo rgyud thams cad bon
NK131(do)003:1483: dang mu stegs kyi phyogs su phul nas rdzogs pa'i
NK131(do)003:1484: sangs rgyas dang theg chen gyi mdo dang rgyud sde
NK131(do)003:1485: thams cad chos ma yin par bsgrubs pa'i snying khams
NK131(do)003:1486: ha cang che ste gsung rab zab mo thams cad
NK131(do)003:1487: dang rgyab 'gal du smra ba 'di 'dra blo dang
NK131(do)003:1488: ldan pa rnams kyis lad mo tsam yang byar mi
NK131(do)003:1489: rung ba'i gnas su rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)003:1490: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi rdzogs rim thams cad sdom
NK131(do)003:1491: pa'i gzhi med par 'gyur ba sogs ha cang nor
NK131(do)003:1492: tshabs che'o // 'di ltar ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK131(do)003:1493: dag pa dngas pa 'od gsal ba //
NK131(do)003:1495: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK131(do)003:1496: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK131(do)003:1499: sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan
NK131(do)003:1500: nas mi 'tshol ba'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par
NK131(do)003:1503: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1504: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK131(do)003:1507: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK131(do)003:1508: gang la srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK131(do)003:1509: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu ma lus ster byed pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1510: yid bzhin nor bu 'dra ba'i sems la 'dud //
NK131(do)003:1512: de nyid dbu ma'i gzhung las kyang gsungs te /
NK131(do)003:1514: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rang bzhin gang //
NK131(do)003:1516: de bzhin gshegs pa rang bzhin med //
NK131(do)003:1518: ces sangs rgyas sems can ngo bo gcig par gsungs pa'i phyir bod kyi blos byas ma yin gyi /
NK131(do)003:1519: bka' dang bstan bcos bsam las 'das pa thams cad
NK131(do)003:1520: mgrin gcig pas sems nyid sangs rgyas su gsungs pas
NK131(do)003:1522: khyed kyi 'dod pa'i sems nyid sangs rgyas ma yin
NK131(do)003:1523: par sgrub byed kyi lung lo brgyar btsal yang bka'
NK131(do)003:1524: mdo rgyud lung man ngag thams cad nas rnyed pa
NK131(do)003:1526: rang sems sangs rgyas yin pa la ngo ma shes
NK131(do)003:1527: pa zhes khrel rgod kyis gnas su byed pa'ang mdo
NK131(do)003:1528: rgyud zab mo'i don la cha med kyi rtags bstan
NK131(do)003:1530: kye ma sems can 'di dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK131(do)003:1531: ye shes yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin mi
NK131(do)003:1532: shes pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyang khong
NK131(do)003:1533: na yod pa ngo mtshar che /
NK131(do)003:1534: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i don ma mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:1535: dper na sems kyi ngo bo gdod nas sangs rgyas
NK131(do)003:1536: yin yang rtsal gyis rang ngo ma shes shing gzung
NK131(do)003:1537: 'dzin ltar snang ba'i rnam rtog las byung ba'i glo
NK131(do)003:1538: bur gyi dri ma bag chags dang bcas pas rang
NK131(do)003:1539: gi ngo bo bsgribs par gyur nas ma mthong ba
NK131(do)003:1540: nyi ma dang sprin sogs dpe dgus rgyal ba byams
NK131(do)003:1541: pas rgyud bla mar gsungs pa bzhin te /
NK131(do)003:1542: 'dir re re nas bris na yi ge mang bar
NK131(do)003:1543: 'gyur phyir bzhag cing shes par 'dod na der ltos
NK131(do)003:1544: shig / slob dpon klu sgrub kyis /
NK131(do)003:1545: gang zhig kun tu ma shes na //
NK131(do)003:1546: srid pa gsum du rnam 'khor ba //
NK131(do)003:1547: sems can kun la des gnas pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1549: ces pa 'di la'ang khyod khrel dgod bya dgos te
NK131(do)003:1550: sems can gyi rgyud la sangs rgyas kyi dbyings nges
NK131(do)003:1551: par gnas rung rnam par rtog pas rang ngo ma
NK131(do)003:1552: shes shing / rmi lam lta bu'i 'khor ba'i snang
NK131(do)003:1553: ba la blos btags pa'i gzung 'dzin ltar snang ba'i
NK131(do)003:1554: chos kyis 'khrul pa 'byams klas su gyur par gsungs
NK131(do)003:1555: shes shing / pa'i phyir / de yang 'phags pa
NK131(do)003:1556: klu'i gsung rab rnams la tshig klog tsam yang ma
NK131(do)003:1557: myong nas sems nyid sangs rgyas su bstan pa 'di
NK131(do)003:1558: rnying ma kho na'i chos su 'dug snyam nas smad
NK131(do)003:1559: pas sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang
NK131(do)003:1560: de dag gi bka' bstan bcos thams cad la skur
NK131(do)003:1561: shes shing / pa'i phyir / ba btab bo //
NK131(do)003:1562: gzhan yang ye shes zhabs kyi 'jam dpal zhal lung
NK131(do)003:1563: shes shing / pa'i phyir / ba btab bo //
NK131(do)003:1564: las kyang / thog med dus nas de las kyang
NK131(do)003:1565: shes shing / pa'i phyir / ba btab bo //
NK131(do)003:1566: las kyang / // rnam rtog chen po'i tshul byung
NK131(do)003:1567: shes shing / pa'i phyir / ba btab bo //
NK131(do)003:1568: las kyang / // ste // de las yang ni
NK131(do)003:1569: shes shing / pa'i phyir / ba btab bo //
NK131(do)003:1571: rlung gi dkyil 'khor nyid byung ste //
NK131(do)003:1573: ma rtogs pas na 'gro ba kun //
NK131(do)003:1576: phyogs kyi glang po rnam rtog ma rig chen po ste /
NK131(do)003:1577: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung byed yin //
NK131(do)003:1578: rnam rtog de dang bral bas na //
NK131(do)003:1579: khyod ni rtag tu mya ngan 'das //
NK131(do)003:1580: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir bka' bstan bcos thams cad du
NK131(do)003:1581: sems nyid sangs rgyas yin yang ngo ma shes pa'i
NK131(do)003:1582: rgyu ni rnam par rtog par gsungs shing rang ngo
NK131(do)003:1583: shes nas sangs rgyas la rang ngo ma shes nas
NK131(do)003:1584: 'khor bar 'khyams pas 'khor 'das gnyis ka rang sems
NK131(do)003:1585: ngo shes ma shes kyi khyad par tsam du gsungs
NK131(do)003:1586: pas / rang chas su yod pa dang sgrub dgos pa yang 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1587: zhes pa'ang kha nas gang byung smras pa ste /
NK131(do)003:1588: khyod cag gis 'khor ba'i rtsa ba ma rig pa yin pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1589: de las ldog pas myang 'das kyi sar phyin pa'i go ba tsam yang rgyud la ma skyes 'dug /
NK131(do)003:1590: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin rang chas su bzhugs kyang
NK131(do)003:1591: de la sgrib byed kyi dri ma glo bur pa'i
NK131(do)003:1592: cha rnam par rtog pa de nyid sbyong ba'i phyir
NK131(do)003:1593: lam bsgom dgos par sangs rgyas kyi gsungs pa 'gog
NK131(do)003:1594: par byed pa re blun te /
NK131(do)003:1596: nyes pa glo bur dang ldan dang /
NK131(do)003:1597: yon tan rang bzhin nyid ldan phyir //
NK131(do)003:1598: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK131(do)003:1599: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK131(do)003:1602: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)003:1603: 'on kyang blo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK131(do)003:1604: de bsal na ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)003:1605: ces gsungs pa 'di khyed cag gis ma mthong bas lan no //
NK131(do)003:1606: rnam rtog gi dri ma sbyong ba'i gnyen por lam
NK131(do)003:1607: mdo sngags gnyis su bstan pa thams cad rigs pa
NK131(do)003:1609: ci yang mi dgos zer ba dang sna tshogs byed pa 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1610: zhes pa'ang chos nyid zab mo'i ngo bo la dgongs nas de skad gsungs pa'i skabs yod de /
NK131(do)003:1612: bsgom med sgom pa po yang med //
NK131(do)003:1613: lha med sngags kyang yod ma yin //
NK131(do)003:1616: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK131(do)003:1617: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK131(do)003:1618: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta //
NK131(do)003:1619: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK131(do)003:1627: zhes bsgrub bya'i chos gang yang med par bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1628: bla ma ya rab chos nyid zab mo'i don mthong
NK131(do)003:1629: ba'i rang ngor mnyam par gzhag pa kho nas sbyin
NK131(do)003:1630: sogs 'dus ma byas kyi tshogs rgya chen po rang
NK131(do)003:1631: bzhin gyis rdzogs pa las sgo gsum 'dus byas kyi
NK131(do)003:1632: bsod nams la ltos mi dgos pa'i tshul /
NK131(do)003:1633: tshangs pa khyad par sems kyis zhus pa las /
NK131(do)003:1634: gang mi 'dzin pa ni sbyin pa'o //
NK131(do)003:1635: mi bsrung ba ni tshul khrims so //
NK131(do)003:1636: mi gnas pa ni bzod pa'o //
NK131(do)003:1637: mi brtson pa ni brtson 'grus so //
NK131(do)003:1638: mi sems pa ni bsam gtan no //
NK131(do)003:1639: mi dmigs pa ni shes rab bo //
NK131(do)003:1642: spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK131(do)003:1643: lha dang sngags ni rnam par gnas //
NK131(do)003:1645: gnas lugs zab mo ma mthong bas sgo gsum bsod
NK131(do)003:1646: nams kyi tshogs la ji ltar 'bad kyang 'khor ba
NK131(do)003:1649: dmus long dmigs bu med pa bye ba khrag khrig rnams //
NK131(do)003:1650: lam yang mi shes grong khyer 'jug par ga la 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1651: shes rab med na mig med pha rol phyin lnga 'di //
NK131(do)003:1652: dmigs bu med pas byang chub reg par nus ma yin //
NK131(do)003:1653: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs shing /
NK131(do)003:1655: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar gyi chos thams cad la
NK131(do)003:1656: blang bar bya ba dang dor bar bya ba'i chos
NK131(do)003:1657: gang yang ma dmigs mi dmigs dmigs par mi 'gyur
NK131(do)003:1658: bar bstan pa ma yin nam /
NK131(do)003:1659: khyod kyis rgyal ba'i yum du blang bya'i chos dang
NK131(do)003:1660: dor bya'i chos 'di dang 'adi'o zhes gsungs pa zhig
NK131(do)003:1661: bstan du yod na ston par gyis shig /'on kyang
NK131(do)003:1662: chos nyid zab mo'i gnas lugs de nyid rtogs pa'i
NK131(do)003:1663: tshe 'dus byas kyi dge bar ltos mi dgos pa
NK131(do)003:1664: la dgongs nas ci yang mi dgos par dam bca'
NK131(do)003:1665: ba rgyal ba'i gsung rab zab mo'i dgongs pa don
NK131(do)003:1666: dam pa'i bden pa dang 'gal ba'i skabs med /
NK131(do)003:1667: de nyid ma rtogs pa'i rigs la rtogs pa'i thabs
NK131(do)003:1668: su sbyin sogs bsod nams kyi tshogs yal bar mi
NK131(do)003:1669: 'dor bas dge ba'i las sna tshogs byed pa yin
NK131(do)003:1670: pas kun rdzob dang 'gal ba'i skabs med med pas
NK131(do)003:1671: bden gnyis blang dor gyi dus skabs mi 'gal bar
NK131(do)003:1673: kun rdzob mtha' gcig la zhen nas don dam pa'i
NK131(do)003:1674: gnas lugs zab mo'i tshig zur tsam yang thos na
NK131(do)003:1675: rna ba 'gebs par byed nas chos kyi sku la
NK131(do)003:1676: skur ba mi bzad pa gdab pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1677: stong pa mtha' gcig tu bzung nas bsod nams kyi
NK131(do)003:1678: tshogs dang rgyu 'bras la rtsis med byed pa'i mtha'
NK131(do)003:1679: gnyis ka la ma lhung ba'i spyod tshul byang chub
NK131(do)003:1680: sems dpa'i gzhung lam ma nor ba yin pas /
NK131(do)003:1681: khyod kyis ci yang mi dgos pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1684: khrel khrel byas pas rgyal ba'i gsung rab zab mo'i
NK131(do)003:1685: don bden pa gnyis ka la yid ma ches shing
NK131(do)003:1687: bla mas ngo sprod nas sangs rgyas rgyu lus yin nam /
NK131(do)003:1688: sems ni sngar nas sangs rgyas tshar bas gsar du sangs rgyas pa 'gal /
NK131(do)003:1689: zhes smra ba 'di gong du bshad pa ltar rdzogs
NK131(do)003:1690: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sems nyid sangs rgyas su mdo
NK131(do)003:1691: rgyud thams cad nas bstan pa khyod kyi blo la
NK131(do)003:1692: mi 'thad par go ba'i log rtog gi gdon chen
NK131(do)003:1693: pos zin par gyur pa ste /
NK131(do)003:1694: 'di ltar dbang dus su sems nyid ngo sprod pa'i
NK131(do)003:1695: skad cig de la rtogs grol dus mnyam du gyur
NK131(do)003:1696: pa o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au ti sogs
NK131(do)003:1697: 'phags yul gyi grub chen ches che ba mang po
NK131(do)003:1698: dang / bod kyi ljongs su mar mi dwags gsum /
NK131(do)003:1701: rnying ma'i zur che chung sogs mngon sum du byung
NK131(do)003:1702: ba so so'i rnam thar gyis shes nus kyang de
NK131(do)003:1703: lta bu mthong ba'i skal ba khyed la med /
NK131(do)003:1704: de rnams kyis lus ma spangs par rdo rje 'chang gi sar gshegs pa'am /
NK131(do)003:1705: lus na bun ltar yal nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1706: sprul pa'i gzugs kyis 'gro don mdzad pa'i ci rigs yod na /
NK131(do)003:1707: khyod kyis bla ma'i man ngag gis ngo sprad pa
NK131(do)003:1708: tsam gyis sangs rgyas ga la srid snyam nas sangs
NK131(do)003:1709: rgyas rgyu lus yin nam sogs kyi gtam 'di rnams
NK131(do)003:1710: don du sems las sangs rgyas 'byung mi srid pa'i
NK131(do)003:1711: sgrub byed du rlom 'dug kyang rigs pa sbyang spyang
NK131(do)003:1712: byas pas nor 'khrul gyi 'dam la zug pa snying
NK131(do)003:1714: rang gi rnam par rtog pas bcings //
NK131(do)003:1715: bdag nyid shes na grol bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1716: zhes pa sogs gong gi lung don rnams la bsam mno thongs shig /
NK131(do)003:1717: des na glo bur gyi dri ma sbyong phyir lam
NK131(do)003:1718: gyi rim pa thams cad sgom pa mdo sngags gnyis
NK131(do)003:1719: ka'i dgongs pa yin zhing dri ma sbyang ba'i gzhi
NK131(do)003:1720: med na sbyangs pa la dgongs pa med de /
NK131(do)003:1722: khams yod na ni las byas pas /
NK131(do)003:1723: sa le sbram dag mthong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1724: khams med na ni las byas pas //
NK131(do)003:1725: nyon mongs 'ba' zhig bskyed par zad //
NK131(do)003:1726: chu shing snying po med do zhes //
NK131(do)003:1727: 'jig rten na ni dper byed kyang //
NK131(do)003:1728: de yi snying po 'bras bu nyid //
NK131(do)003:1729: mngar po za bar byed pa ltar //
NK131(do)003:1730: snying po med pa'i 'khor ba las //
NK131(do)003:1731: nyon mongs gzeb dang bral gyur na //
NK131(do)003:1732: de yi snying po sangs rgyas nyid //
NK131(do)003:1733: lus can kun gyi bdud rtsir 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1734: zhes dpe'i sgo nas gsungs pa ltar gzhi'i dus su
NK131(do)003:1735: sems can la sangs rgyas bzhugs kyang mngon du ma
NK131(do)003:1736: gyur pa sems rtog glo bur ba'i sgrib byed kyi
NK131(do)003:1737: dri ma'i sbubs su chud pa sa 'og gi gser
NK131(do)003:1738: sogs dpe don du ma sbyar bas rgyal ba'i bka'
NK131(do)003:1740: klu sgrub sogs kyis rgya cher bstan pa ma mthong
NK131(do)003:1741: 'dug pa da ni de rnams la thos pa mang
NK131(do)003:1742: du btsal nas chos mig dag pa sgrubs dang phyogs
NK131(do)003:1743: re'i 'ching ba dam po'i sgrog tu tshud pa 'di
NK131(do)003:1745: 'di ltar mdo lam du'ang dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten
NK131(do)003:1746: nas byang chub tu sems bskyed pa nas bzung zhi
NK131(do)003:1747: lhag gi ting nge 'dzin la bslab pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1748: sngags su bla ma sangs rgyas kun 'dus su shes
NK131(do)003:1749: pa'i dad pas bsten nas dbang dang rim gnyis sgom
NK131(do)003:1750: pa thams cad rang sems sangs rgyas su ngo 'phrod
NK131(do)003:1751: thabs ma yin na gzhan gyi dgos pa ci yod
NK131(do)003:1752: smros shig / rgya bod kyi grub thob tshad ldan
NK131(do)003:1753: thams cad rang sems sangs rgyas yin pa la glo
NK131(do)003:1754: bur gyi dri mas mngon du ma gyur pa dri
NK131(do)003:1756: gsang sngags kyi myur lam la bslabs nas grol ba
NK131(do)003:1757: sha stag byung ba bla ma'i man ngag gis rang
NK131(do)003:1758: sems sangs rgyas su ngo 'phrod nas sangs rgyas pa
NK131(do)003:1759: yin la / gzhan du de kho na nyid ni
NK131(do)003:1760: bla ma'i man ngag kho nas rtogs par bya dgos
NK131(do)003:1761: yin la / kyi / rtog ge'i rigs pas ni
NK131(do)003:1762: nam yang rtogs par gsungs shing khyed cag gis bla
NK131(do)003:1763: ma'i gdams ngag ngan skyugs kyi phung po ltar bltas
NK131(do)003:1764: nas chos nyid zag mo'i gnas blo tshod kyis gzhal
NK131(do)003:1765: nas rtogs par rlom pa'i blo rtse gtad phyogs drag
NK131(do)003:1766: shos des kyang rlom tshod tsam du 'gro ba dka'
NK131(do)003:1767: yin la / kyi / ste / rigs par smra
NK131(do)003:1768: ba yongs kyi gtsug gi nor bu slob dpon chos
NK131(do)003:1769: yin la / kyi / ste / kyi grags pas / de nyid du zhi tshol 'dod pas //
NK131(do)003:1770: rjes dpag gtan tshigs brten mi byed //
NK131(do)003:1771: legs par bsgoms pas myong 'gyur gyi //
NK131(do)003:1772: de rjes dpag mchan yis rang rig rtogs pa min //
NK131(do)003:1773: de nyid don gyi snying po ni //
NK131(do)003:1774: rjes dpag shes pas nyams myong min //
NK131(do)003:1775: bla ma bzang po bstan byas nas //
NK131(do)003:1776: bsgoms pas nyams su myong bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1777: zhes de kho na nyid gsal bar gsungs shing /
NK131(do)003:1779: slob dpon ye shes zhabs kyis /
NK131(do)003:1780: de 'dra rab mchog ye shes ni //
NK131(do)003:1781: mngon sum tshogs pas mi shes so //
NK131(do)003:1782: de bzhin dpyad mkhan gyis mi shes //
NK131(do)003:1783: mi shes 'khrul pas rab g.yogs pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1784: nyan thos kyis kyang mi shes so //
NK131(do)003:1787: slob dpon b+ha bya'i zhal nas /
NK131(do)003:1788: rtog bcas rtog pa med pa yi //
NK131(do)003:1789: shes pa gnyis kyis 'di mi rtogs //
NK131(do)003:1790: sgra dang tshad ma'i tha snyad dag /
NK131(do)003:1791: de don sgom la dgos pa med //
NK131(do)003:1792: ji ltar mun pa'i nang gi rdzas //
NK131(do)003:1793: 'ol tshod dag tu tshol ba bzhin //
NK131(do)003:1794: de bzhin rjes su dpag pas kyang //
NK131(do)003:1795: de bzhin don ni shes mi 'gyur //
NK131(do)003:1797: jo bo rje'i bden gnyis 'jug pa las kyang /
NK131(do)003:1798: rtog ge thams cad mi mthun pas //
NK131(do)003:1799: tshad mas 'jal ba'i chos nyid kyang //
NK131(do)003:1800: mang po nyid du mi 'gyur ram //
NK131(do)003:1801: mngon sum rjes dpag dgos pa med //
NK131(do)003:1803: dbu ma rin po che'i sgron ma las kyang /
NK131(do)003:1804: de nyid dang ni bsgrub bya ste //
NK131(do)003:1805: rtog ge pa yi yul ma yin //
NK131(do)003:1806: nor bu rin chen brtag pa la //
NK131(do)003:1807: long ba tshad ma yin nam ci //
NK131(do)003:1808: zhes pa sogs rgya cher bstan pas rtog ge'i rigs
NK131(do)003:1809: pas dpyad pas chos nyid dam pa'i bden pa'i gnas
NK131(do)003:1810: lugs mi rtogs par rnam pa du mas gsungs shing
NK131(do)003:1811: / de bzhin rtogs par rlom pa la gnod byed
NK131(do)003:1812: ldog tu med par bka' stsal ba nyid kyis gzhung
NK131(do)003:1813: lugs mang po ma gzigs pa'i skyon tsam du zad
NK131(do)003:1814: / la / chos nyid don dam pa'i gnas lugs
NK131(do)003:1815: de nyid bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas rtogs
NK131(do)003:1818: gang gis brjod min lhan cig skyes //
NK131(do)003:1819: nam du yang ni rnyed min te //
NK131(do)003:1820: bla ma'i dus thabs man ngag dang //
NK131(do)003:1821: bdag gi bsod nams las shes bya //
NK131(do)003:1824: bla ma'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i //
NK131(do)003:1825: sgom pa de ni sgom par 'os //
NK131(do)003:1827: 'phags pa lha'i ye shes snying po kun las btus par /
NK131(do)003:1828: de phyir phyogs ni gnyis po yang //
NK131(do)003:1829: skems shing yongs su skems pa ni //
NK131(do)003:1830: mkhas pa'i go 'phang mchog phra ba //
NK131(do)003:1831: bla ma'i kha las rtogs par bya //
NK131(do)003:1834: 'di ni thog ma med dus nas //
NK131(do)003:1835: rang bzhin yang dag rtag zlo yang //
NK131(do)003:1836: bla ma yang dag ma bsten na //
NK131(do)003:1840: gsal zhing rab dga' nam mkha' 'dra //
NK131(do)003:1841: rang byung lhag pa'i lha chen po //
NK131(do)003:1842: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK131(do)003:1843: bla ma'i kha las rtogs par bya //
NK131(do)003:1844: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang chen 'di //
NK131(do)003:1845: nam mkha' nam mkha'i spyod yul lo //
NK131(do)003:1846: 'di yi don shes brgyud pa yi //
NK131(do)003:1847: bla ma dam pa rtag bkur bas //
NK131(do)003:1848: u dum+bar lta brgya lam na //
NK131(do)003:1849: bsod nams can gyis skad cig shes //
NK131(do)003:1850: zhes pa sogs tshad ma'i lung mtha' yas shing don
NK131(do)003:1851: de ltar rgya bod kyi mkhas grub tshad ldan thams
NK131(do)003:1852: cad kyis thugs nyams su bzhes shing phyag len du
NK131(do)003:1854: gzhan yang rdzogs chen gyi lam 'dir rang byung gnyug
NK131(do)003:1855: ma'i de kho na nyid rang rgyud la gnas pa
NK131(do)003:1856: bla ma'i man ngag gis bcar phog tu ngo 'phrod
NK131(do)003:1857: cing rtogs pa ji lta ba mngon gyur gyi tshe
NK131(do)003:1858: chos thams cad kyi gting sleb ces grub thob rnams
NK131(do)003:1859: bzhed cing sa lam rim bgrod las 'das pa bya
NK131(do)003:1860: bral lhun grub chen po'i lta sgom mchog gzigs yongs
NK131(do)003:1861: kyi nges pa'i gsang tshig ste /
NK131(do)003:1862: mkhas mchog n+aa ro pan chen gyis de kho na sgrub pa'i thabs su /
NK131(do)003:1863: ma bcos rim pa'i ting 'dzin gsal //
NK131(do)003:1864: bya ba med bzhin don kun rdzogs //
NK131(do)003:1865: rang byung gnyug ma kun gyi gzhi //
NK131(do)003:1866: bgrod med rnal 'byor lhun grub lam //
NK131(do)003:1868: rdzogs pa'i ye shes snying po la //
NK131(do)003:1869: rim pa'i lam med mthar phyin pa //
NK131(do)003:1870: zhes gsungs pa sogs do ha dang man ngag thams
NK131(do)003:1871: cad kyi dgongs pa dbyangs gcig mgrin gcig tu grub
NK131(do)003:1872: pas bod kyis blos byas ma yin pa'ang shes nus
NK131(do)003:1873: la / des na sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa'i
NK131(do)003:1874: lung bka' mdo rgyud thams cad dang bla mas sems
NK131(do)003:1875: nyid sangs rgyas su ngo sprod pa'i gdams ngag thams
NK131(do)003:1876: cad la log par blta zhing sems nyid ngo 'phrod
NK131(do)003:1877: pa'i thabs dang ye shes la /
NK131(do)003:1878: lta ba log par 'dzin par 'gyur ba dang /
NK131(do)003:1879: mu stegs kyi lta ba dang mtshungs pa'i tha chad
NK131(do)003:1880: kyi lta ba zhes su smra ba 'dis ni rgyu'i
NK131(do)003:1881: theg par 'khor lo bar mtha' gnyis kyi dgongs pa
NK131(do)003:1882: dang / sngags kyi rgyud sde thams cad dang /
NK131(do)003:1883: khyad par du dbang gi ye shes dang /
NK131(do)003:1884: gnyug ma'i sems phyag rgya chen po dang rim pa gnyis pa'i lam thams cad dang /
NK131(do)003:1885: rdzogs pa'i rim pa khyad par can grub thob yongs
NK131(do)003:1886: kyi dgongs nyams mngon par rtogs pa'i yon tan thams
NK131(do)003:1887: cad la skur pa mi bzad pa btab pa'i las
NK131(do)003:1888: ngan gyi phung po ni gzugs su grub na nam
NK131(do)003:1889: mkha' snod du chung ba tsam bsags 'dug pas thar
NK131(do)003:1890: 'dod rnams kyis 'di 'dra'i gtam la yid ches lta
NK131(do)003:1891: ci rjes zlos tsam du'ang byar mi rung zhing shin
NK131(do)003:1892: tu ya nga ba'i gnas su mthong ngo //
NK131(do)003:1894: rje ngag dbang byams pa de nyid bshes gnyen chen
NK131(do)003:1895: por grags pas gsung 'di rnams dgongs pa can los
NK131(do)003:1896: yin mod / gal te nges pa'i dbang du yin
NK131(do)003:1897: na khong la'ang rtog ge'i shan gyis cung zad gos
NK131(do)003:1898: pa 'dra zhing rgyu des rjes 'jug blun po mkhas
NK131(do)003:1899: pa'i go sar 'gying ba rnams chos spong ba'i las
NK131(do)003:1900: la 'jug par mthong bas kyang bstan pa'i byi dor
NK131(do)003:1902: des na rtog dpyod kyis rten 'byung gi de nyid
NK131(do)003:1903: rtogs par rloms pa kho na las rgyud sde rnams
NK131(do)003:1904: kyi nges gsang zab mo'i gdams pa dang bla ma'i
NK131(do)003:1905: man ngag rang gis ma myong ba rgyu mtshan du
NK131(do)003:1906: bkod nas de dag la zhe sdang ba'i gtam smra
NK131(do)003:1907: ba ni rigs pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)003:1909: gser bzang ma thob skye bo 'ga' //
NK131(do)003:1910: gshol po mi rung smra zhing smod //
NK131(do)003:1911: ces pa kho na dran to //
NK131(do)003:1913: rdzas dang sngags kyi sgo nas phyag rjes 'jog pa
NK131(do)003:1914: mang du 'ong ba'i grub rtags kyi tha snyad chen
NK131(do)003:1915: po mi yongs / las kyi mngon shes dang rdzu
NK131(do)003:1916: 'phrul yi dwags dang bar do dang dud 'gro sogs
NK131(do)003:1917: po mi yongs / la'ang yod / sgom stobs kyis
NK131(do)003:1918: thob pa'i mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul phyi rol mu
NK131(do)003:1920: rang cag rnams kyis kyang mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul
NK131(do)003:1921: ting nge 'dzin brtan po thob pa'ang grangs las 'das
NK131(do)003:1922: kyang 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin la ci yang
NK131(do)003:1923: ma gnod pa ma zad grogs su song ba red
NK131(do)003:1924: / thos rtags zhi zhing dul ba yin //
NK131(do)003:1925: sgom rtags nyon mongs med pa yin //
NK131(do)003:1926: zhes dam pa gang ma'i gsungs la byung ba'i grub
NK131(do)003:1927: rtags kyi gtso bo rang gi rgyud kyi chags sogs
NK131(do)003:1928: nyon mongs rtsa ba ni zad pa dang je chung
NK131(do)003:1929: je chung du song ba dang /
NK131(do)003:1930: sems rgyud je bzang je bzang du song ba zhig la zer ba red /
NK131(do)003:1932: 'jig rten pa rnams rdzas sngags la brten nas rkang
NK131(do)003:1933: lag gi rjes 'jog par smra ba'i cal sgrog gi
NK131(do)003:1934: rjes su khyed rang 'brangs par 'dug ste /
NK131(do)003:1936: rgya gar sogs su rdzas kyi bcud len grub na lus mi snang ba 'grub par bshad cing /
NK131(do)003:1937: de'ang rgyud sde rnams su gsungs pa'i las tshogs yin /
NK131(do)003:1938: de bzhin du lta stangs grub pa'ang bsad bskrad rengs pa sogs kyi las gang 'dod 'grub par dang /
NK131(do)003:1939: de las gso bar nus pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1940: grub pa'i rdzas kyis reg pa'i dngos po thams cad
NK131(do)003:1941: gser du bsgyur ba sogs las de dang de'i grub
NK131(do)003:1943: 'on kyang las chen brgyad sogs thun mong gi dngos
NK131(do)003:1944: grub yin yang des bstan pa dang sems can mtha'
NK131(do)003:1945: yas pa'i don du 'gyur phyir byang chub myur du
NK131(do)003:1946: 'grub pa'i nye rgyur song ste gsang sngags thabs mang
NK131(do)003:1947: ba dang myur ba 'di lta bu la ngos mi
NK131(do)003:1949: dper na 'phags pa klu sgrub dang bi r+au pas
NK131(do)003:1950: gser 'gyur rtsis sa steng gi dge 'dun la 'tsho
NK131(do)003:1951: ba sbyar zhing sems can mang po dbul phongs kyi
NK131(do)003:1953: grub chen rnams kyi lta stangs sogs kyis gdul bya mtha' yas pa'i don mdzad pa bzhin no //
NK131(do)003:1954: khyed cag gis sgom stobs kyi mngon shes dang rdzu
NK131(do)003:1955: 'phrul gyi rol pa la'ang yod ces sangs rgyas pa'i
NK131(do)003:1956: theg pa che chung gi lam lnga'i yon tan rnams
NK131(do)003:1957: phyi rol pa dang mtshungs par khas blangs shing /
NK131(do)003:1958: phyi rol pa'i mngon shes sogs 'dir smra don med /
NK131(do)003:1959: nang pa'i gang zag sgom stobs kyis mngon shes dang
NK131(do)003:1960: rdzu 'phrul thob pa zhig gis bdag 'dzin ma spangs
NK131(do)003:1962: mig gis gzugs phra rags thams cad mthong yang da
NK131(do)003:1963: dung sgrib byed ma spangs zhes smra ba dang khyad
NK131(do)003:1964: ci yod / lam lnga'i gnas skabs su chags sogs
NK131(do)003:1965: nyon mongs pa ji tsam 'grib pa de tsam du
NK131(do)003:1966: lam rtags kyi yon tan 'phel ba chos nyid yin
NK131(do)003:1967: pas spangs rtogs kyi yon tan du rlung ltar grags
NK131(do)003:1968: ci yod / pa yin la / theg chen gyi
NK131(do)003:1969: tshogs lam chen po nas spyan dang mngon shes thog
NK131(do)003:1970: mar 'byung ste chos rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin 'thob
NK131(do)003:1971: cing sprul pa'i sku las chos nyan nus par bshad
NK131(do)003:1972: de lha'i mig gi mngon shes dang rna ba'i mngon
NK131(do)003:1974: de nyid sbyor lam drod thob pa nas brtsams gsal brtan du 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)003:1975: mthong lam thob nas dus gcig la lus brgya sprul pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1976: sangs rgyas brgya mthong ba dang /
NK131(do)003:1977: sems can brgya'i don nus pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1978: sems kyi rtog pa brgya shes pa dang /
NK131(do)003:1979: zhing brgya bgrod pa sogs yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis la dbang sgyur zhing /
NK131(do)003:1980: sa gnyis pa yan du snga ma las phyi ma brgya 'gyur gyi yon tan gsungs pa sogs dang /
NK131(do)003:1981: sha'i spyan dang rdzu 'phrul phal pa ni 'jig rten pa'i bsam gtan gyis kyang 'grub par bshad pa'o //
NK131(do)003:1982: theg pa che chung gi lam rtags zad par gyi
NK131(do)003:1983: skye mched lus 'byung bzhir bsgyur ba sogs mtha' yas
NK131(do)003:1984: shing / de ma rtogs par khyod kyis sangs rgyas
NK131(do)003:1985: kyi bstan pa'i lam lnga'i yon tan rnams mu stegs
NK131(do)003:1986: kyi lugs dang mtshungs par bsams shing 'phags pa mngon
NK131(do)003:1987: shes rdzu 'phrul mnga' ba rnams kyis bdag tu 'dzin
NK131(do)003:1988: pa la gnod par ma nus par smra ba rnams
NK131(do)003:1989: ni rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che chud zos
NK131(do)003:1990: su gtong ba'i gtam 'di 'dra snyigs ma'i yang mthar
NK131(do)003:1991: chos min chos su bardzu nas thub bstan rin po
NK131(do)003:1993: lam lnga'i mngon rtags mu stegs kyi mngon shes rdzu 'phrul dang khyad gnam sa lta bu yod cing /
NK131(do)003:1995: nyan rang gi 'phags pa'i mngon shes rdzu 'phrul cha
NK131(do)003:1996: shas phra mo tsam la'ang 'jig rten pa'i ston pa
NK131(do)003:1997: lha chen po dang khyab 'jug sogs kyis rdul tsam
NK131(do)003:1998: yang 'gran par mi nus na kun tu rgyu rnams
NK131(do)003:2000: de lta bus bdag med tsam yang ma rtogs par smra ba de las tha chad ci yod /
NK131(do)003:2001: yang khyod kyis nyon mongs pa zad pa grub rtags
NK131(do)003:2002: su smras nas mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul grub rtags
NK131(do)003:2003: su mi 'dod pa rang la med pa rtags su
NK131(do)003:2004: bkod pa las nyon mongs zad pa zhig la mngon
NK131(do)003:2005: shes dang rdzu 'phrul med pa ga la srid /
NK131(do)003:2006: rtags de rnams nyon mongs zad nas ye shes 'phel
NK131(do)003:2007: ba'i lag rjes yin pa'i phyir me yod na du
NK131(do)003:2008: ba med pa srid dam shes par gyis shig /
NK131(do)003:2009: sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)003:2011: grub thob thams cad kyis nyon mongs pa spangs nas
NK131(do)003:2012: rdzu 'phrul dang mngon par shes pa rgya chen po
NK131(do)003:2013: la dbang thob pa yin pa ma go bar zad
NK131(do)003:2014: cing sems rgyud bzang ba tsam grub rtags su 'dod
NK131(do)003:2015: na bstan pa la ma zhugs pa'i 'jig rten pa'i
NK131(do)003:2016: skye bo mang zhig kyang grub thob tu thal te
NK131(do)003:2017: / tha mal pa la sems rgyud bzang po lhan
NK131(do)003:2018: skyes su yod pa mang du yod pa'i phyir ro
NK131(do)003:2019: / // 'di rnams rang la mngon rtags de rnams
NK131(do)003:2020: rus sbal gyi spu ltar dkon par gyur pa ston
NK131(do)003:2021: pa'i zhar la 'phags pa rnams kyi mngon shes dang
NK131(do)003:2022: rdzu 'phrul mthu chen po rnams la skur pa btab
NK131(do)003:2023: par 'gyur ram mi 'gyur shes ldan rnams kyis dpyod
NK131(do)003:2024: / // dang / yi dwags dang bar srid dang
NK131(do)003:2025: dud 'gro sogs la'ang mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul yod
NK131(do)003:2026: ces rigs mtshungs par khas blangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:2027: rgyud zhi dul du 'gyur ba'ang thos pa kho nas
NK131(do)003:2028: min te sems rgyud grol ba las byung ba yin
NK131(do)003:2029: pas ma sgom gyi yon tan du byed dgos /
NK131(do)003:2030: thos pa phal cher nyon mongs dang bag med kyi
NK131(do)003:2031: grogs su song ba mang ste chos la sdang ba'ang
NK131(do)003:2032: rgyud ma grol bar thos pa tsam gyis khengs shing
NK131(do)003:2033: mngon pa'i nga rgyal la bdag tu bltas pa'i skyon
NK131(do)003:2034: te legs pa'i skar ma bzhin du thos pas ngan
NK131(do)003:2035: 'gror bskyur ba'i lo rgyus mang ngo //
NK131(do)003:2037: sgra snyan ngag rtsis sa ris bzo lag shes sogs
NK131(do)003:2038: shes byas gnas tsam yin pa'i de rnams shes pa
NK131(do)003:2040: 'on kyang phyi nang thun mong ba'i rig gnas yin
NK131(do)003:2041: pa'i de dag la mkhas pa phyi rol mu stegs
NK131(do)003:2043: dud 'gro'i skye gnas su gyur pa'i 'bu srin tshun
NK131(do)003:2044: chad kyi rig gnas de rnams la mkhas pa grangs
NK131(do)003:2045: med pa ma byas pa med /
NK131(do)003:2046: rang cag tshos kyang de dag la mkhas par byas
NK131(do)003:2047: pa grangs las 'das kyang 'khor bas mthar bar ma
NK131(do)003:2048: zad cung zad 'phar ma thub pa red /
NK131(do)003:2049: de rnams sangs rgyas pa'i thabs su dngos gzhi ni
NK131(do)003:2050: lta zhog thar pa tsam thob pa'i thabs dngos gzhi
NK131(do)003:2051: min par ma zad ngan song las thar pa'i thabs
NK131(do)003:2053: sngon du rig pa'i gnas rnams la mkhas par byas
NK131(do)003:2054: pa zhig phyis 'bu srin sogs su skye bar smras
NK131(do)003:2055: pa'ang brtag par bya dgos te /
NK131(do)003:2056: rig gnas de tsam la mkhas pa'i shes rab des
NK131(do)003:2057: blang dor gyi gnas cung zad tsam yang ma 'byed
NK131(do)003:2058: pa 'gal zhing gal te mu stegs sogs yin yang
NK131(do)003:2059: mngon mtho tsam zhig mi 'grub mi srid de /
NK131(do)003:2061: gang gang pa yi las byas pas //
NK131(do)003:2062: 'bras bu de lta nyid du smin //
NK131(do)003:2063: zhes gsungs pas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i khyad par
NK131(do)003:2064: rgyu 'bras kyi rnam gzhag 'chol bar 'gyur te rig
NK131(do)003:2065: pa'i gnas de tsam la ma rmongs pa'i shes rab
NK131(do)003:2066: de dud 'gror skye ba'i rgyur song bas rnam smin
NK131(do)003:2068: snga ma de tsam du mkhas pa zhig 'bu srin
NK131(do)003:2069: du skyes pa'i tshe de'i rgyud la rgyu mthun gyi
NK131(do)003:2070: 'bras bu mi srid par thal te /
NK131(do)003:2072: rig pa nangs par 'chi yang slobs //
NK131(do)003:2073: tshe 'dir mkhas par ma gyur kyang //
NK131(do)003:2074: skye ba phyi mar bcol ba yi //
NK131(do)003:2075: nor la rang nyid len dang mtshungs //
NK131(do)003:2076: zhes pa'i 'gal ba spong dka' zhing //
NK131(do)003:2077: 'bu srin du skyes pa de'i rgyud la rig pa'i
NK131(do)003:2078: gnas shes pa'i bag chags gtan med pa'i phyir ro
NK131(do)003:2079: // gzhan yang mdo sde rgyan las /
NK131(do)003:2080: rig pa'i gnas lnga dag la mkhas par ma byas na /
NK131(do)003:2081: 'phags mchog gis kyang thams cad mkhyen nyid mi 'gyur te /
NK131(do)003:2082: de lta bas na gzhan dag tshar gcod rjes 'dzin dang /
NK131(do)003:2083: bdag nyid kun shes bya phyir de la de brtson bya /
NK131(do)003:2084: zhes byang chub sems dpas rig pa'i gnas de rnams
NK131(do)003:2085: la ma sbyangs na 'phags pa mchog thob kyang thams
NK131(do)003:2086: cad mkhyen par mi 'gyur zhes gsungs shing thams cad
NK131(do)003:2087: mkhyen pa'i nye rgyu rig gnas rnams la mkhas par
NK131(do)003:2088: bya dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)003:2089: khyed kyis thar pa'i rgyu tsam du'ang mi 'gro bar khas blangs pa'i 'gal ba 'di ji ltar spong /
NK131(do)003:2091: rgyal sras rnams kyis mi slob pa'i //
NK131(do)003:2092: dngos de dag yang yod ma yin //
NK131(do)003:2093: de ltar gnas pa'i mkhas pa la //
NK131(do)003:2094: bsod nams mi 'gyur gang yang med //
NK131(do)003:2097: ma bslabs pa la kun mkhyen du //
NK131(do)003:2099: zhes kun mkhyen thob pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo rig pa'i gnas mtha' dag la slob par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)003:2101: de bzhin gshegs pa dus mkhyen rgyal po ni //
NK131(do)003:2102: snyan ngag mkhan tshe bde gshegs rtsam mchog la //
NK131(do)003:2103: tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyis bstod nas kyang //
NK131(do)003:2104: dang por byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK131(do)003:2105: zhes gsungs pas snyan ngag gi bstod pa tshigs su
NK131(do)003:2106: bcad pa gcig tsam yang byang chub thob pa'i rgyur
NK131(do)003:2107: song na rig lam rnams la mkhas pa'i bya ba
NK131(do)003:2108: 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum gyis bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)003:2109: sems can gyi don rlabs po che sgrub pa sangs
NK131(do)003:2110: rgyas kyi rgyur mi 'gro bar khas blangs pa 'dis
NK131(do)003:2111: sangs rgyas dang byang sems gtsug lag gi gzhung thams
NK131(do)003:2112: cad la skur pa btab pas las ngan tshan po
NK131(do)003:2115: sgom na thos pa mi dgos zhes //
NK131(do)003:2116: blun po thos rgya chung rnams smra //
NK131(do)003:2117: thos pa med pa'i sgom pa ni //
NK131(do)003:2119: zhes sa pan gyi gsung drangs nas gong du rig
NK131(do)003:2120: pa'i gnas thams cad mi dgos shing spang chog par
NK131(do)003:2121: khas blangs / yang de ma thag tu thos pa
NK131(do)003:2122: dgos par smra ba'i 'gal ba ltag sprod 'di 'dra
NK131(do)003:2124: thos pa 'di'i thog mar yang rig gnas la sbyangs
NK131(do)003:2125: par ma byas pas ji lta bar 'jug pa'i thabs
NK131(do)003:2126: med de / tha na yi ge'i brda dag dang
NK131(do)003:2127: ming tshig tha snyad kyi gnas tsam la'ang rmongs bzhin
NK131(do)003:2128: du gsung rab kyi don shes pa lta zhog /
NK131(do)003:2129: tshig tsam la'ang nor 'khrul gyi 'og nas ldang bar mi nus shing /
NK131(do)003:2130: des na thos pa'i rgyu rig pa'i gnas rnams la
NK131(do)003:2131: sbyangs pa'i shes rab kyis gsung rab kyi tshig don
NK131(do)003:2132: yongs su thos pa la 'jug par byed pas mkhas
NK131(do)003:2134: brda sprod sogs rig gnas rnams la than du lta
NK131(do)003:2135: zhing thos pa dgos par smra ba'ang rgyu med pa'i
NK131(do)003:2136: 'bras bu la re ba tsam ste /
NK131(do)003:2137: rang gis ma shes pa rgyu mtshan du byas nas
NK131(do)003:2138: rig lam chen po rnams la skur pa gdab pas
NK131(do)003:2139: skye bo rnams lam log par sbyar bar mi bya'o
NK131(do)003:2141: sangs rgyas nas bzung bar ma chad pa'i snyan brgyud
NK131(do)003:2142: kyi man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla ma zhig las
NK131(do)003:2143: thos dgos kyi / rim brgyud kyi man ngag med
NK131(do)003:2144: pa'i bshad nyan ni bum stong gcig nas gcig byo
NK131(do)003:2146: gnam yig dang lung bstan yin zer nas gzhan la
NK131(do)003:2147: ston pa'i skad byed pa ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK131(do)003:2149: zhes rgyal dbang lnga pa chen po'i gsung zhig kyang drangs so //
NK131(do)003:2150: gnam chos zhes pa sngon lha tho tho ri snyan
NK131(do)003:2151: shal la pang kong phyag rgya pa gnam nas babs
NK131(do)003:2152: pa'i chos yin 'dug pa thams cad kyis tshad mar
NK131(do)003:2154: dag snang gi chos la gnam chos su btags pa srid cing /
NK131(do)003:2156: 'phags yul gyi grub thob mchog gzigs rnams la rgyud sde so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang /
NK131(do)003:2157: bla ma dngos sam ye shes kyi sku bstan nas /
NK131(do)003:2158: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
NK131(do)003:2159: gdams pa dang rjes su gdams pa bstan pa nyams
NK131(do)003:2160: su blangs nas grub pa thob pa 'ba' zhig yin
NK131(do)003:2161: pas rgyun de la tshad mar 'dod dgos shing /
NK131(do)003:2162: de bzhin du bod ljongs su byung ba'i dag snang
NK131(do)003:2163: gi chos rnams kyang bla ma dang lhag pa'i lhas
NK131(do)003:2164: stsal pa kho nar grub pas ye shes kyi sku
NK131(do)003:2165: las lhag pa'i lha dang bla ma gzhan ci dgos
NK131(do)003:2166: / da lta'i rgyun nyams pa med par bzhugs bzhin du snyan brgyud kyi man ngag ci la chad /
NK131(do)003:2167: sngon gyi skyes bu dam pa rnams la yongs su
NK131(do)003:2168: grags pa'i bka' brgyud dang sgrub brgyud rnams kyang de
NK131(do)003:2170: bka' srol de la da lta'i dus lta bu'i sa
NK131(do)003:2171: skya'i bla ma zhig gis rdul tshon sogs dkyil 'khor
NK131(do)003:2172: chol le ba zhig i thon mi thon bltas /
NK131(do)003:2173: cho ga zhig blo bshar byas nas snod min 'ba'
NK131(do)003:2174: zhig la gsang sgrogs gang thub thub cig byed pa'i
NK131(do)003:2175: dbang brgyud dang / dpe la bltas pa'i tshig nyog
NK131(do)003:2176: gi bshad yam gyu ru lugs kyi rgyud bshad khul
NK131(do)003:2177: de 'dra dgos pa ma yin pas tha mal gyi
NK131(do)003:2178: rnam rtog dang sgo bstun pa 'khrul lo //
NK131(do)003:2179: yang gnam chos dang lung bstan gyis chos zhes pa'ang gter ma la bsams na /
NK131(do)003:2180: byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams la /
NK131(do)003:2181: sa rdo ri brag shing sogs gnas gang nas kyang dam pa'i chos 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK131(do)003:2182: bcom ldan 'das kyis bsod nams thams cad sdud pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK131(do)003:2183: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid /
NK131(do)003:2184: chos 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK131(do)003:2185: gus pa dang bcas pa rnams ni 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan na 'dug kyang /
NK131(do)003:2186: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis zhal ston par mdzad cing chos kyang thos par mdzad do //
NK131(do)003:2187: dri ma med pa'i gzi brjid chos 'dod pa'i byang
NK131(do)003:2188: chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi chos
NK131(do)003:2189: kyi gter ri dang ri sul dang shing gi nang
NK131(do)003:2190: na bcug pa dag yod do //
NK131(do)003:2191: gzungs dang chos kyi sgo mtha' yas pa glegs bam
NK131(do)003:2192: du byas pa dag kyang lag tu 'ong bar 'gyur
NK131(do)003:2193: ro // zhes gter gyi chos 'don pa po sangs
NK131(do)003:2194: rgyas rnams kyis zhal ston cing chos kyang ston par
NK131(do)003:2195: ro // mdzad do // zhes gsungs na bcom ldan
NK131(do)003:2196: 'das kyis so skye'i bla ma zhig gi go chod
NK131(do)003:2198: de bzhin du bum pa dang ka ba las kyang chos 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK131(do)003:2200: phyi ma de tshe dus dag chu //
NK131(do)003:2201: dge slong dgra bcom zhes bya ba //
NK131(do)003:2203: sngon ni des ni gang bshad pa'i //
NK131(do)003:2204: theg pa chen po'i mdo sde yang //
NK131(do)003:2205: de yi tshe na bum pa las //
NK131(do)003:2206: dka' thub chen po dran par byed //
NK131(do)003:2207: glegs bam de la de bltas nas //
NK131(do)003:2208: de la sngags ni zlos pa na //
NK131(do)003:2209: zhes lung bstan pa bzhin dge slong dgra bcom par
NK131(do)003:2210: grags pas bum pa bzang po zhig nas mdo la
NK131(do)003:2211: sogs pa'i chos gang 'dod bton nas nyams su blang
NK131(do)003:2212: ba'i lo rgyus kyang chos 'byung mang por 'byung /
NK131(do)003:2213: mdo sde mdzang blun du khyim bdag cig gi khyim
NK131(do)003:2214: gyi ka ba las bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'i
NK131(do)003:2215: cho ga thon pa'i lo rgyus kyang snang ba'i phyir
NK131(do)003:2216: ro // de bzhin du dpal mchog gi rgyud las kyang /
NK131(do)003:2217: rgyud dang rgyud kyi rgyal po gang //
NK131(do)003:2218: phyag na rdo rje khyod nyid kyis //
NK131(do)003:2219: gter nas gter du phyungs ste stsal //
NK131(do)003:2221: gter chos thams cad rnying chos dang gter ma 'don
NK131(do)003:2222: mkhan thams cad zog po rdzun ma yin mi dgos
NK131(do)003:2224: dge lugs pa'i chos lugs ni sprang kha 'du byas pa lta bu ma yin /
NK131(do)003:2225: zhes pa chos lugs mang po la bsams nas smras na /
NK131(do)003:2226: bod kyi ljongs su sangs rgyas pa'i lugs gcig kho na las gzhan ni med /
NK131(do)003:2227: de'ang ston pa gcig gi bstan pa yin te /
NK131(do)003:2228: da lta'i bon po ni bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya
NK131(do)003:2229: bzhi dang mi 'gal bas nang bar bsdu rung zhing
NK131(do)003:2230: / bstan pa de la 'dod tshul tha dad ni mang ste /
NK131(do)003:2231: nyan thos kyi theg pa kho na la'ang sde pa bco brgyad byung bas mtshon no //
NK131(do)003:2232: des na mdo sngags so so'i bzhed pa tha dad
NK131(do)003:2233: kyi bka' srol las byung ba'i gdams ngag thams cad
NK131(do)003:2234: la sna res chog shes ma mdzad cing gsan bsam
NK131(do)003:2235: gyis sgro 'dogs chod par mdzad pa ni rgya gar
NK131(do)003:2236: dang gangs can gyi mkhas grub spyi'i rnam thar lags
NK131(do)003:2237: na rje btsun blo bzang grags pas kyang bod kyi
NK131(do)003:2238: ljongs tsam du grags pa'i gdams ngag ma lus pa
NK131(do)003:2239: gsan nas thugs nyams su bzhes pa'i tshul rnam thar
NK131(do)003:2240: 'dun legs ma sogs su gsal ba'i phyir de dag
NK131(do)003:2241: sprang kha 'du lta bur 'gyur ram soms /
NK131(do)003:2243: dge lugs pa'i chos ni mdo sngags kyi bstan pa
NK131(do)003:2244: la 'jug pa'i sgo zhugs nas nyams su len pa'i
NK131(do)003:2245: rim pa lus kyi cha lugs /
NK131(do)003:2246: 'gro 'chag nyal 'dug gi spyod lam tha na bza'
NK131(do)003:2247: btung la spyod tshul rnams kyang dam tshig dang sdom
NK131(do)003:2248: pa bsrungs tshul sha stag yin /
NK131(do)003:2249: zhes sogs nyag nyog mang po zhig bris so //
NK131(do)003:2250: de khyed rang mthong thos rgya chung bas lan pa tsam ste /
NK131(do)003:2251: chos kyi ngos na de lta bu re gsar rnying thams cad nas ma bshad pa gang yang med /
NK131(do)003:2252: da lta'i dus su gang zag gis de ltar mi
NK131(do)003:2253: byed pas chos nas bshad pas phan ma thogs te
NK131(do)003:2254: / chos dang gang zag 'dzol bar song ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:2256: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK131(do)003:2257: sogs bstan pa thams cad kyi sdoms su gsungs pa'i
NK131(do)003:2258: shwa lo ka de thams cad kyi kha nas lta
NK131(do)003:2260: don rgyud la zhugs pa ni bka' ste rang rgyud
NK131(do)003:2261: la sdo ba grang byed cing mdzub mo btsugs dgos
NK131(do)003:2262: te ltar snang dang tshul 'chos su ma song bar
NK131(do)003:2263: tshig 'di yi don lag len du thebs nges byed
NK131(do)003:2264: pa zhig srid na rjes su yi rang ba las
NK131(do)003:2265: kyang yi rang ba phul lo //
NK131(do)003:2266: yang mi la yab sras sogs tshad ldan du brjod nas /
NK131(do)003:2267: de dag gi brgyud 'dzin kar stag 'bri gung sogs
NK131(do)003:2268: de dang mi mthun par smras shing bka' gdams pa
NK131(do)003:2269: nam mkha' 'bum gyi dris lan sa pan gyi gsung
NK131(do)003:2270: drangs 'dug kyang / de lta bu sh+aakya sh+r+ai'i 'khor
NK131(do)003:2271: pan chung bi b+h+au tis kyang 'bri gung 'jig rten
NK131(do)003:2272: drangs 'dug kyang / mgon po la / phyag rgya pa 'di kun zob che //
NK131(do)003:2273: zhes sogs smad pas pan chen gyis khyod kyis sdig chen po bsags /
NK131(do)003:2274: mgon po klu sgrub la skur pa btab ces bshags
NK131(do)003:2275: pa byed bcug pa bzhin dus skabs der bka' brgyud
NK131(do)003:2276: ya bzhi dar che bas gnam gyis sa bkab pa
NK131(do)003:2277: lta bur byung bas rang phyogs kyi kha 'dzin tsam
NK131(do)003:2278: mam dgongs pa can du shes dgos shing bka' gdams
NK131(do)003:2279: pa la'ang pha dam pa sogs kyis dgag par mdzad
NK131(do)003:2280: pa sogs dang / sa skya pa rang gi lam
NK131(do)003:2281: 'bras la'ang 'gos lhas btsas dpon slob kyis dgag pa
NK131(do)003:2282: byas pas mtshon 'di 'dra'i rigs zur za tsam gyis
NK131(do)003:2283: chos min du sgrub mi nus pa gong du smras
NK131(do)003:2286: de skabs su sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa nyams dma'
NK131(do)003:2287: ba'i dus yin pa sa skya ba la dga' rab
NK131(do)003:2288: dar / bar skabs su ma rtog log rtog gi
NK131(do)003:2289: dri ma rnams rje bla mas bsal bar mdzad nas
NK131(do)003:2290: dri ma med pa'i thub pa mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK131(do)003:2291: pa yongs rdzogs deng sang dga' ldan la dar ba
NK131(do)003:2292: dar / 'di yin / de las gzhan na med /
NK131(do)003:2294: stag tshang lo ts+aas basngagasa pa'i tshigs bcad sogs bris so //
NK131(do)003:2295: skabs der bod ljongs 'dir bstan pa shin tu dar zhing /
NK131(do)003:2296: mar mi'i bka' brgyud las grub thob kyi tshang chen po rdol zhing /
NK131(do)003:2297: 'bri stag tshal pa khro phu kar 'brug 'ba' ro
NK131(do)003:2298: ma sogs dang 'brug pa gcig la'ang stod smad par
NK131(do)003:2299: gsum dang / bka' gdams pa'i sde yang bsam las 'das par bzhugs shing /
NK131(do)003:2300: rnying ma la'ang so zur gnubs sogs bshad sgrub 'dzin pa shin tu mang ba dang /
NK131(do)003:2301: sa skya pa la'ang stod smad kun tu dar rgyas
NK131(do)003:2302: che ba dang rgya gar gyi pan+di ta dang bod
NK131(do)003:2303: kyi lo ts+aa ba mang zhing mkhas pa dang grub
NK131(do)003:2304: pa thob pa shin tu mang ba dus gcig tu
NK131(do)003:2305: byon pas bstan pa nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i
NK131(do)003:2306: skabs yin te / khyod kyis chos 'byung deb ther sogs ma mthong 'dug pa'i skyon du snang ngo //
NK131(do)003:2307: stag tshang lo ts+aas rje rin po che'i grub mtha'
NK131(do)003:2308: la skyon gyi khur chen bco brgyad 'phangs pa grub
NK131(do)003:2309: mtha' kun shes su gsal bas tshigs su bcad pa
NK131(do)003:2310: de ngo bsrung tsam las nges par ci'i phyir yin
NK131(do)003:2313: 'jam dbyangs sprul pa blo bzang zhes sogs dang /
NK131(do)003:2314: pad+ma bka' yi thang yig las /
NK131(do)003:2315: dge ldan zhes bya'i dgon gnas dam pa ru sogs dang /
NK131(do)003:2316: gsang mtshan las rab rdo rje bde ba rtsal zhes bris pa /
NK131(do)003:2317: khyed rang gis gong du lung bstan gyi chos dang
NK131(do)003:2318: thang yig dang 'dra 'bag rnams rdzun du khas blangs
NK131(do)003:2319: zin cing / 'dir rje rin po che tshad mar
NK131(do)003:2320: sgrub byed du thang yig dang lung bstan drangs pa
NK131(do)003:2321: rang tshig snga phyi 'gal ba'i smyon gtam lta bu
NK131(do)003:2322: la su zhig tshad mar byed de bzhad gad kyi
NK131(do)003:2324: 'on kyang rje rin po che ni lung bstan du
NK131(do)003:2325: mas zin cing slob dpon pad+ma'i sprul par gsungs pa'i
NK131(do)003:2327: rjes 'brangs kyi skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis kyang de ltar bzhed de /
NK131(do)003:2328: pan chen blo bzang chos kyi rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK131(do)003:2330: rnam 'phrul dpal ldan mar me mdzad //
NK131(do)003:2331: yang sprul blo bzang grags pa'i dpal //
NK131(do)003:2332: khyod min bdag la skyabs gzhan gang //
NK131(do)003:2334: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad bka' bgros nas //
NK131(do)003:2335: bod yul rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba dang //
NK131(do)003:2336: log 'dren sde brgyad srin po'i kha gnon mdzad //
NK131(do)003:2337: o rgyan rin po che la gsol ba 'debs //
NK131(do)003:2338: zhes sogs mang du gsungs shing gzhan yang smos kyis mi lang ngo //
NK131(do)003:2340: khyed kyis rdzogs chen sogs snga 'gyur chos min du
NK131(do)003:2341: nan gyis bsgrubs 'dug pa de tsam du rang lugs
NK131(do)003:2342: kyi chos phugs sun phyung pa yin te /
NK131(do)003:2343: rje tsong kha pa'i thun mong min pa'i bla ma
NK131(do)003:2344: lho brag nam mkha' rgyal mtshan zhes pa yi dam
NK131(do)003:2345: gsang ba'i bdag po dang mi'i lab pa bzhin bzhugs
NK131(do)003:2346: pa de nyid la rje rin po ches bod kyi
NK131(do)003:2347: chos lugs so so'i lta ba'i dogs pa bcad pa
NK131(do)003:2348: de nyid kyis yi dam la zhus pa'i dris lan
NK131(do)003:2350: yab kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa /
NK131(do)003:2351: yum kun tu bzang mo'i snying gtam /
NK131(do)003:2352: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gi gsang tshig /
NK131(do)003:2354: sman chen po sgrub pa la sems nyid 'od gsal rtsad chod /
NK131(do)003:2355: ces gsungs shing kun bzang yab yum ni yod med
NK131(do)003:2356: gang ltar khyod rang rnams med par khas blangs pa
NK131(do)003:2357: de yin zhing / rnying ma'i chos phugs su gsang
NK131(do)003:2358: ba'i bdag po'ang bzhugs 'dug pas des rdzun mi gsung
NK131(do)003:2359: de yin zhing / las che / yang las kyi rdo rje /
NK131(do)003:2360: rig pa'i ngo bo stong pa 'di /
NK131(do)003:2364: ye gdod ma nas gnas pa yin gsungs /
NK131(do)003:2365: 'di la bcas bcos ma byed pa kho rang gang
NK131(do)003:2366: 'dug gi steng du zhog dang gol sa de ka
NK131(do)003:2367: dag gi klong du sangs rgyas pa yin gsungs /
NK131(do)003:2368: de bzhin du rang bzhin 'od gsal ba 'di /
NK131(do)003:2369: ye nas stong pa dang dbyer med du lhun gyis grub /
NK131(do)003:2371: gang shar kyang rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa gsum zung 'jug chen por shes par gyis dang /
NK131(do)003:2372: dbyer med du sangs rgyas pa yin gsungs /
NK131(do)003:2374: phyag na rdo rje'i bskyed rdzogs bdud rtsi'i thigs pa las /
NK131(do)003:2376: skye med blo 'das chos kyi dbyings //
NK131(do)003:2377: 'gag med spros bral cir yang snang //
NK131(do)003:2379: rang snang skye med dbyings su thim //
NK131(do)003:2382: stong nyid sgom pa gol ba'i gnas //
NK131(do)003:2383: stong nyid blo dang ma bral na //
NK131(do)003:2384: gnyis snang chos kyis grol mi nus //
NK131(do)003:2385: sku lnga bsgrub byar 'dod pa dang //
NK131(do)003:2386: dug lnga spang byar 'dod pa dang //
NK131(do)003:2387: sangs rgyas thob byar 'dod pa dang //
NK131(do)003:2389: dgag sgrub der 'dzin ma chod na //
NK131(do)003:2390: yang dag snying po'i don mi rnyed //
NK131(do)003:2393: blo 'das tsam la blo zhen kyang //
NK131(do)003:2394: blos byas chos kyis grol mi nus //
NK131(do)003:2395: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK131(do)003:2396: blo zad chos zad theg pa'i rtse //
NK131(do)003:2397: rang sems chos sku dngos med la //
NK131(do)003:2398: rig pa'i ming 'dogs ma mdzad cig /
NK131(do)003:2399: blta ru med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK131(do)003:2400: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK131(do)003:2401: smra bsam brjod med ngang la zhog /
NK131(do)003:2402: blo las 'das pa'i ngang la zhog /
NK131(do)003:2403: byar med ngang la lhug par zhog /
NK131(do)003:2404: zhog ces bya ba blo yi tshig /
NK131(do)003:2405: zhog dang ma zhog tha snyad med //
NK131(do)003:2406: ming med brjod med brtag gzhi bral //
NK131(do)003:2407: rtags snang blo ni dbyings su zhi //
NK131(do)003:2408: dgag sgrub spang len klong du yal //
NK131(do)003:2409: sprin tshogs mkha' la dngas pa 'dra //
NK131(do)003:2410: rnam rtog ma spangs rang sar dag /
NK131(do)003:2411: lar ni lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi //
NK131(do)003:2412: lta ba zhe 'dod med par gyis //
NK131(do)003:2413: sgom pa blo sgom 'dzin pa zhig /
NK131(do)003:2414: spyod pa zhen med byar med skyongs //
NK131(do)003:2415: 'bras bu chos skur rang chas la //
NK131(do)003:2416: gzhan nas sgrub 'dod yid smon dor //
NK131(do)003:2417: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa'i chos //
NK131(do)003:2418: rgyud 'grel man ngag brjod mi lang //
NK131(do)003:2419: de dag thams cad 'dus pa'i bcud //
NK131(do)003:2420: mar gyi yang zhun lta bu yi //
NK131(do)003:2421: man ngag bdud rtsi thigs pa 'di //
NK131(do)003:2423: snod mchog gser bum lta bu yi //
NK131(do)003:2424: las kyi rdo rje khyod la byin //
NK131(do)003:2425: zhes pa la sogs bka' mdo rgyud lung man ngag /
NK131(do)003:2426: lta ba dang grub mtha' thams cad kyi snying po
NK131(do)003:2427: dang yang snying rdzogs pa chen po kho nar dgongs
NK131(do)003:2428: nas tshig gi sgo nas kyang dmar khrid rjen par
NK131(do)003:2429: gtan la phab pa'i rdzogs chen gyi chos skad grub
NK131(do)003:2430: mtha' gzhan dang ma 'dres par yod cing gong du
NK131(do)003:2431: dri ba pos khregs chod thod rgal gyi gnas lugs
NK131(do)003:2432: ci 'dra snyam pa ni grub chen la gsang ba'i
NK131(do)003:2433: bdag pos gdams pa'i chos skor 'di nyid la rtog
NK131(do)003:2434: dpyod zhib tu gyis dang rtogs par yod do //
NK131(do)003:2435: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgom spyod 'bras tshad ma
NK131(do)003:2436: nor bar bla ma'i man ngag gis ngo sprod pa'i
NK131(do)003:2437: tshul de lta bu rje tsong kha pa la rjes
NK131(do)003:2438: su gdams pa'i chos su grub pa'i phyir rje rin
NK131(do)003:2439: po che ni grub chen las kyi rdo rje'i thugs
NK131(do)003:2440: sras su tshad mas grub pa dang /
NK131(do)003:2441: rje de nyid rgyal bstan ris med kyi bshes gnyen
NK131(do)003:2442: chen por bzhugs pas bod kyi mkhas pa gzhan ltar
NK131(do)003:2443: su la'ang zur za bar mi mdzad cing gangs can
NK131(do)003:2444: ljongs su grags pa'i rgyal bstan thams cad nyams bzhes
NK131(do)003:2445: kho nar snying po dril te phyag len du btab
NK131(do)003:2448: bstan pa thams cad 'gal med rtogs pa dang //
NK131(do)003:2449: gsung rab ma lus gdams par 'char ba dang //
NK131(do)003:2450: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i mthar thug rtogs pa dang //
NK131(do)003:2451: nyes spyod chen po'i g.yang sa las kyang srung //
NK131(do)003:2452: zhes pa 'di kho na nyams su bzhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:2453: don 'di la rjes 'jug tu khas che ba rnams
NK131(do)003:2454: kyis cung zad rtog dpyod dgos pa 'dra zhig 'dug
NK131(do)003:2455: ste bstan pa'i gnad gsang thams cad la skyon gyi
NK131(do)003:2456: gnas tshol ba'i rnam rig kho nar sgrims shig /
NK131(do)003:2457: ces ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)003:2458: de bzhin du rdzogs chen dang phyag chen la nyams
NK131(do)003:2459: bzhes snying por mdzad pa'i tshul yang rje'i sgrub brgyud
NK131(do)003:2460: kyi bstan pa'i bdag po gung ru rgyal mtshan bzang
NK131(do)003:2461: po dang rtogs ldan 'jam dpal rgya mtsho dag gis
NK131(do)003:2462: gsungs shing / lcang skya thams cad mkhyen pa rol pa'i rdo rjes /
NK131(do)003:2463: rje rin po che'i rnam thar zhal gsung mar rdzogs
NK131(do)003:2464: chen nyams bzhes mdzad tshul rgyas par yod pas phyis
NK131(do)003:2465: kyi gang zag rnams chos spong las bzlog phyir khong
NK131(do)003:2466: gis nan gyis btsal yang rnyed ma thub ces gsungs
NK131(do)003:2467: pa tshad ma'i ngag las thos shing phyogs lhung can
NK131(do)003:2468: 'dras snga mo zhig nas mi mngon par byas pa
NK131(do)003:2469: gor ma chags / gzhan yang rgyal ba dge 'dun
NK131(do)003:2470: rgya mtshos nyang gter drag dmar dang byang gter drag
NK131(do)003:2471: mthing la thugs dam mdzad cing /
NK131(do)003:2472: bsod nams rgya mtshos bla ma gsang 'dus kyi tshes bcu sogs thugs dam dang /
NK131(do)003:2473: yon tan rgya mtshos kyang gshed skor la brtson pa
NK131(do)003:2474: cher mdzad pa so so'i rnam thar gyis shes la
NK131(do)003:2475: / kun mkhyen lnga pa chen pos gong du brjod
NK131(do)003:2476: pa'i snga 'gyur gyi yongs 'dzin de dag las rnying
NK131(do)003:2477: ma bka' gter bod du rgyun bzhugs so cog gsan
NK131(do)003:2478: cing nyams su bzhes pa'i tshul rnam thar bu sti
NK131(do)003:2479: gsum dang gsan yig gang+g+aa'i chu rgyun glegs bam gnyis
NK131(do)003:2480: pa gsum pa bzhi pa rnams su ltos dang gsal
NK131(do)003:2481: / lo // khyad par chos nyid bar do la
NK131(do)003:2482: rdzogs chen lhun grub kyi lam ma gtogs gdams pa
NK131(do)003:2483: gzhan gyis go chod pa zhig dka' bar 'dug ces
NK131(do)003:2484: ched du brjod cing nyams bzhes kyi mthil du mdzad
NK131(do)003:2485: nas 'jam dpal rdzogs chen dang thugs rje chen po
NK131(do)003:2486: 'khor ba dbyings sgrol gyi khrid yig rgyas par mdzad
NK131(do)003:2487: / lo // pa sogs dang / thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi gsung las /
NK131(do)003:2488: 'khor med drin las khregs chod thod rgal gyi //
NK131(do)003:2489: zab mo'i lam bzang mngon sum bstan pa'i mthus //
NK131(do)003:2490: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol rang rig tu //
NK131(do)003:2491: 'phrod pas dad pa dbyar mtsho lta bur 'phel //
NK131(do)003:2493: sangs rgyas gzhan nas re ba'i mkhas rlom gyis //
NK131(do)003:2494: stong bshad shar 'drer nub tu glud gtong tshul //
NK131(do)003:2495: mthong tshe zag bcas phung po 'od sku ru //
NK131(do)003:2496: grol 'di gsang chen rnying ma'i khyad par chos //
NK131(do)003:2498: de bzhin du pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa blo bzang chos rgyan gyis /
NK131(do)003:2499: g.yung ston rdo rje dpal zhes rnying ma'i sngags 'chang
NK131(do)003:2500: chen po de nyid kyi skye bar zhal gyis bzhes
NK131(do)003:2501: pa skyes rab gsol 'debs su gsal ba ltar dang
NK131(do)003:2502: / des mdzad pa'i phyag chen las /
NK131(do)003:2503: rdzogs chen phyag chen dbu ma dang //
NK131(do)003:2504: lam 'bras gcod yul zhi byed sogs //
NK131(do)003:2505: so so'i ming 'dogs mang na yang //
NK131(do)003:2506: nyams len can gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NK131(do)003:2507: dpyad na dgongs pa gcig tu 'bab //
NK131(do)003:2509: lcang skya'i skye ba gong mar bzhed pa pha bong
NK131(do)003:2510: kha pa dpal 'byor lhun grub kyis phyag chen rdzogs
NK131(do)003:2511: chen dbu ma gsum gcig tu ngo sprod pa snyan
NK131(do)003:2512: brgyud lta ba spyi khyab ces pa'i khrid yig mdzad
NK131(do)003:2513: pa da lta gra sa chen po rnams su dge
NK131(do)003:2514: bshes chos mthun gzur gnas rnams 'chad nyan mdzad bzhin
NK131(do)003:2515: pa yin la / de'i phyir smra ba ngan pa'i
NK131(do)003:2516: yig dum 'dis rang lugs kyi brgyud phugs rnams dgra
NK131(do)003:2517: yi dngas mar bzung nas sma phab pa yin te
NK131(do)003:2518: pa yin la / / khyod kyis chos log tu
NK131(do)003:2519: yang yang smras pa'i rdzogs chen la lho brag grub
NK131(do)003:2520: chen dang rgyal ba yab sras sogs thugs dam gyi
NK131(do)003:2522: des na rje sa pan gyis /
NK131(do)003:2523: mgo bo bcad nas rnga ma'i rgyan //
NK131(do)003:2524: smyon pa min pa su zhig byed //
NK131(do)003:2525: ces pa'i thog tu babs par shes so //
NK131(do)003:2527: dam chos dga' ba'i ro myong ba'i na dga' ldan pa dang /
NK131(do)003:2528: thog mtha' bar gsum du dag gi bar spyod pa'i na dge ldan pa zer ba red /
NK131(do)003:2529: sogs kyi don dang mi 'brel pa'i brjod bya mang tsam dang /
NK131(do)003:2530: rang bzhin ri la bskor ba byed pa'i phan yon
NK131(do)003:2531: yod pa'i mdo rgyud khugs ma mthong bas rnam bshad
NK131(do)003:2532: byed pa nyes dmigs che ba'i bdag gis zer tshod
NK131(do)003:2534: rang bzhin gyi ri yin tshad la skor ba byas pas phan yon thob par sus ma bshad /
NK131(do)003:2535: gnas chen rnams la skor ba dang mchod pa sogs
NK131(do)003:2536: byas na bsod nams bshad tshod bzhin los kyang thob
NK131(do)003:2537: ste mdo glang ri lung bstan dang /
NK131(do)003:2538: bal yul rang byung mchod rten gyi sngon rabs dang /
NK131(do)003:2539: bde mchog sogs rgyud sde rnams su sangs rgyas dang
NK131(do)003:2540: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i
NK131(do)003:2541: tshogs kyi bzhugs gnas dang pho brang du gsungs pa
NK131(do)003:2542: kho nas chog cing skor ba'i phan yon sogs dngos
NK131(do)003:2543: bstan du ma gsungs kyang dkon mchog gi rten bzhugs
NK131(do)003:2544: pa'i gtsug lag khang la bskor bas /
NK131(do)003:2545: phan yon rgya cher 'byung ba yin na dngos su
NK131(do)003:2546: bzhugs pa'i gnas las phan yon ci yi phyir mi
NK131(do)003:2547: 'byung ste / rigs pas kyang 'grub sla bar ma
NK131(do)003:2548: zad mchog gzigs rnams kyis gnas yig dang phan yon
NK131(do)003:2549: mdzad 'dug pa la byis pa'i skye bos brgal bar
NK131(do)003:2552: yon tan 'dod pa nags na gnas pa yis //
NK131(do)003:2553: pha rol dag gis skyon la brtags mi bya //
NK131(do)003:2554: bdag ni khyad par 'phags shing bdag mchog ces //
NK131(do)003:2555: de snyam du ni sems bskyed mi bya'o //
NK131(do)003:2556: zhes bris 'dug pa 'di la dpyad nas kyang rang
NK131(do)003:2557: nyid kyis kha 'dzin pa'i chos dang grub mtha' 'di
NK131(do)003:2558: nyid kho na mchog ces gzhan mkhas grub kyi skyes
NK131(do)003:2559: bu ji snyed kyi nyams bzhes rma med pa'i dam
NK131(do)003:2560: pa'i chos mdo sngags kyi gsang ba zab mo la
NK131(do)003:2561: chos ma yin par smra ba mi rigs shing tshul
NK131(do)003:2562: de dag gis rang nyid kyis chos spangs shing gzhan
NK131(do)003:2563: dag de la sbyor ba'i nyes pa ni brjod pa'i
NK131(do)003:2566: mtshams med lngas ni chos spang bar 'gyur ba 'di yi gzugs brnyan tsam du'ang mi spyod do //
NK131(do)003:2568: chos spong ba'i bsam pa 'di skad du /
NK131(do)003:2569: 'di la khyed dang bdag cag gis bslab par mi bya ste /
NK131(do)003:2572: 'di ni ston pa'i bstan pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)003:2573: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)003:2574: zhes zer zhing de bdag nyid kyang spangs la gzhan dag la yang mos pa med par byed cing /
NK131(do)003:2575: bdag gzhan gyis bsam pa nyams par byed pa bdag gzhan chud gsan par dga' ba /
NK131(do)003:2576: bdag nyid kyang phyir spong bar 'dod la /
NK131(do)003:2577: gzhan yang spang du 'jug pa chos 'jig pa'i las
NK131(do)003:2578: bsags pa de'i gzugs brnyan du yang 'gyur re kan
NK131(do)003:2579: / zhes sogs mdo rgyud bstan bcos thams cad nas
NK131(do)003:2580: mtha' yas par gsungs kyang yi ges 'jigs pas bzhag
NK131(do)003:2581: / go // mjug 'dir yang yid la mi 'bab
NK131(do)003:2582: pa'i 'ga' zhig 'dug kyang don chung bas ma bris
NK131(do)003:2583: / go // so // lar yi ge 'di'i mgo
NK131(do)003:2584: mjug thams cad du yig sdeb ma dag cing rnam
NK131(do)003:2585: dbye log pa sogs kyis don mi go ba dang
NK131(do)003:2586: / go // so // / don gyi gnas la
NK131(do)003:2587: go rgya chung ba'i gtam 'ba' zhig la lan gyi
NK131(do)003:2588: rnam pa 'dri ba dus dang snag shog gron tsam
NK131(do)003:2589: las dgos don che bar ma mthong bas blo dman
NK131(do)003:2590: rnams the tshom gyi gnas las bzlog phyir skyon gang
NK131(do)003:2591: che'i skabs rnams la 'gal spong cung zad bris pa
NK131(do)003:2594: skye dgu'i bsod nams snyigs ma'i mtha' ru lhung //
NK131(do)003:2595: dpang gyur skyes bu nam langs skar ma bzhin //
NK131(do)003:2596: rnam par dpyod pa'i mig kyang zums gyur na //
NK131(do)003:2597: ngan rtog rnams kyis thub bstan cis mi dkrugs //
NK131(do)003:2598: gnag rdzi rgan po las kyang tha chad pa'i //
NK131(do)003:2599: gyi na'i gtam dang rmongs pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK131(do)003:2600: chos dang chos min 'byed rlom 'di 'dra'i dus //
NK131(do)003:2601: rgyal ba'i bstan pa ci phyir nyams mi dma' //
NK131(do)003:2602: chos min gtam gyis chos kun 'gog byed cing //
NK131(do)003:2603: chos ltar bcos pas gzhan mgo gdugs ltar bskor //
NK131(do)003:2604: chos la sdang ba'i sdig 'dra gzhan med pas //
NK131(do)003:2605: chos 'dod rnams kyis 'di la 'jigs par gyis //
NK131(do)003:2606: sngags sogs zab mo'i chos la rgyab phyogs pas //
NK131(do)003:2607: rtsa ltung phal cher khur du bzhes gyur te //
NK131(do)003:2608: gzugs brnyan tsam gyi rdo rje'i theg pa ni //
NK131(do)003:2609: dbang gzhu'i 'jo sgeg lha yi lam du bzhin //
NK131(do)003:2610: yang dag gnas la som nyi'i dri ma yis //
NK131(do)003:2611: zab don gzugs brnyan 'char ba'i skabs dben na //
NK131(do)003:2612: theg chen sde snod byad dang mi mdza' ba'i //
NK131(do)003:2613: rnam dpyod 'khar ba'i +aa dar+sha des ci //
NK131(do)003:2614: tshul khrims lta dang brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin gyi //
NK131(do)003:2615: bdag lta'i tshang tshing kun nas rgyas gyur der //
NK131(do)003:2616: gcig tu zhi ba'i sman ljongs kyis btang bas //
NK131(do)003:2617: 'gog lam bden pa'i bsti gnas gang du mchis //
NK131(do)003:2618: legs cha cung zad tsam la'ang bdag gir bgyid //
NK131(do)003:2619: nyes tshogs ji snyed gzhan phyogs la bslan pa'i //
NK131(do)003:2620: gzu bor mi gnas gtam gyi ca co'i sgras //
NK131(do)003:2621: spros bral sems kyang zhi ba'i mnal las dkrogs //
NK131(do)003:2622: de phyir rtsod pa kun bral lung gi rnga //
NK131(do)003:2623: rigs pa'i sbyor bas legs bshad sgra bsgrags pas //
NK131(do)003:2624: 'khyal gtam rdul phran mtha' dag lhung gyur kyang //
NK131(do)003:2625: gzhan thugs 'khrugs par gyur kun snying nas mthol //
NK131(do)003:2626: tshad mar gyur pa rgyal gsung ji bzhin du //
NK131(do)003:2627: legs par 'doms pa'i dge ba gang thob des //
NK131(do)003:2628: tshul bzhin yang dag lta la kun zhugs nas //
NK131(do)003:2629: mtha' yas srid mtsho pha mthar rgal gyur cig /
NK131(do)003:2630: ces brag dkar dge bshes zhes bya bas dris lan
NK131(do)003:2631: du btags pa'i snga 'gyur rnying ma'i chos la lung
NK131(do)003:2632: rigs kyi dgag bya 'gog byed gang yang med bzhin
NK131(do)003:2633: du 'jig rten pa'i ngan shags lta bu'i smra ba
NK131(do)003:2634: ngan pa 'ga' zhig mthong bas blo chung bsod nams
NK131(do)003:2635: dman pa cha shas log lta la sbyar bar srid
NK131(do)003:2636: pas / de dag las bzlog 'dod kyi bsam pa
NK131(do)003:2637: kho nas sangs rgyas gnyis pa 7o rgyan rin po
NK131(do)003:2638: che'i rjes 'jug tu rlom pa'i rnying ban rgan po
NK131(do)003:2639: gyi na pa 7nges don bstan 'phel zhes bgyi bas
NK131(do)003:2640: rang gnas 'od bzang nyi ma'i rdzong du bris pa
NK131(do)003:2641: yongs la phan par gyur cig //
